[2026-02-18 07:33:59] [INFO] Product variant images has been updated - Shopidy ID - 10201309806906 - BC id=115 => {"product":{"id":10201309806906,"title":"2.8k Type Room Temperature Sensor","body_html":"\u003Ch3\u003EEasy temperature monitoring\u003C\/h3\u003E\n\u003Cul\u003E\n\u003Cli style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003EMeasures temperature from 0\u00b0 to 120\u00b0F | -17\u00b0 to 49\u00b0C\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003ERequires additional accessory wire to connect Sensaphone\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003EFor use in clean, indoor environments\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003C\/ul\u003E\u003Cp style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003EThe Room Temperature Sensor can be used with most Sensaphone models to measure the temperature in a clean dry environment. The Sensaphone will trigger an alarm when the temperature falls outside of the programmed high or low temperature limit. The sensor is mounted on a flat surface anywhere ambient air temperatures need to be measured and connects to the Sensaphone with optional accessory wire.\u003C\/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan\u003EThis model is recommended to be located in clean, dry environment. For outdoor use model FGD-0101 is recommended.\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/p\u003E\n\u003Ch3\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E\u003C!-- pagebreak --\u003E\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/h3\u003E\n\u003Ch3\u003E\u003Cspan\u003ETechnical Specifications\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/h3\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\"vouter\"\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\"vcenter col-1\"\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003ESensor Temperature Range:\u003C\/strong\u003E 0\u00b0 to 120\u00b0F | -17\u00b0 to 49\u00b0C\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\"vouter\"\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\"vcenter col-1\"\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EAccuracy:\u003C\/strong\u003E 1\u00b0F | .56\u00b0C\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\"vouter\"\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\"vcenter col-1\"\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EConnection:\u003C\/strong\u003E Hardwired\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\"vouter\"\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\"vcenter col-1\"\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EDimensions:\u003C\/strong\u003E 2.5 x .75 x .75 | 35 x 19 x 19mm\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\"vouter\"\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\"vcenter col-1\"\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003ESensor Series:\u003C\/strong\u003E 2.8K Series\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\"vouter\"\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\"vcenter col-1\"\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003ENotes:\u003C\/strong\u003E Not for outdoor use\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\"vcenter col-1\"\u003E\u00a0\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003Ch3 class=\"vcenter col-1\"\u003EDownloads\u003C\/h3\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\"vcenter col-1\"\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0987\/4738\/4122\/files\/FGD-0100_CS.pdf\"\u003E2.8k Type Room Temperature Sensor Sales Brochure\u003C\/a\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Ca href=\"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0987\/4738\/4122\/files\/LIT-0037%20instructions.pdf\"\u003E2.8k Type Room Temperature Sensor Instructions\u003C\/a\u003E\n\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003C\/div\u003E","vendor":"Sensaphone","product_type":"physical","created_at":"2026-02-18T01:33:57-05:00","handle":"28k-type-room-temperature-sensor","updated_at":"2026-02-18T01:33:57-05:00","published_at":"2026-02-18T01:33:55-05:00","template_suffix":null,"published_scope":"global","tags":"BRAND__Sensaphone, CAT__Temperature Sensors__VAL, MAINSKU__FGD-0100, OLD__115__ID, TYPE__physical","status":"active","admin_graphql_api_id":"gid:\/\/shopify\/Product\/10201309806906","variants":[{"id":53038630469946,"product_id":10201309806906,"title":"Default Title","price":"30.00","position":1,"inventory_policy":"continue","compare_at_price":null,"option1":"Default Title","option2":null,"option3":null,"created_at":"2026-02-18T01:33:57-05:00","updated_at":"2026-02-18T01:33:58-05:00","taxable":true,"barcode":"","fulfillment_service":"manual","grams":454,"inventory_management":"shopify","re