[2026-02-18 07:40:33] [INFO] Product variant images has been updated - Shopidy ID - 10201312231738 - BC id=118 => {"product":{"id":10201312231738,"title":"Ethernet-to-WiFi Adapter Accessory","body_html":"\u003Ch3 style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003EAdd connectivity to any network based Sensaphone\u003C\/h3\u003E\n\u003Cul\u003E\n\u003Cli style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003EConnect any network based Sensaphone to WiFi\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003EWeatherproof housing allows unit to be mounted outdoors\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003EUsers program the adapter to connect with a WiFi network via downloadable software\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003EThe distance between the adapter and router is limited by the strength of the WiFi network, however, much farther distances can be achieved by using another adapter to strengthen the WiFi signal\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003EUsers program the adapter to connect with a WiFi network via downloadable software\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003C\/ul\u003E\u003Cp style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003EThe Ethernet-to-WiFi Adapter can be used with all wired network based Sensaphone models to provide WiFi access. The adapter allows you to place your Sensaphone in a location where the required Ethernet connection may not be available, but a WiFi signal is available. The unit features an IP65-Rated weatherproof housing that ensures continued operation in harsh outdoor environments or in climates of extreme cold, heat, or continuous moisture. The kit also contains a power supply and pole or wall mounting hardware. It is connected to the Sensaphone\u00a0remote monitoring system\u00a0via an Ethernet cable (not included).\u003C\/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003E\u003C!-- pagebreak --\u003E\u003C\/p\u003E\n\u003Ch3 style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003ETechnical Specifications\u003C\/h3\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003E\u003C