[2026-02-18 07:41:22] [INFO] Product variant images has been updated - Shopidy ID - 10201312624954 - BC id=120 => {"product":{"id":10201312624954,"title":"Sensaphone Stratus EMS Monitoring System","body_html":"\u003Cul\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003EA supervised internet connection assures the Stratus EMS is online and monitoring at all times\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003EStore your sensor readings in the cloud to automatically protect against data loss and provide limitless information storage\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003ENotifies an unlimited number of people by e-mail, text message or voice phone calls in the event of an alarm\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003EPoll Modbus registers from other equipment via RS485 and TCP\/IP\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003E12 universal digital or analog inputs with available 24VDC (50mA) per zone to monitor temperature, humidity, water and mor\u003C\/span\u003Ee\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003ETemperature sensing range of -109\u00b0 to 168\u00b0F | -85\u00b0 to 76\u00b0C\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003EManage multiple units, make programming changes and access status conditions using a simple, powerful web-based interface\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003EFits in a 1U rack space\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003EUp to 30 hours of extended battery backup life\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E2 relay outputs for manual or automatic switching\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003EAPI Data Interchange Formats: JSON, HTTPS, POST, REST web services, cURL\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003EAbility to use Sensaphone WEB600 and WSG30 as expansion modules\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003C\/ul\u003E\u003Cp\u003ESensaphone\u2019s cloud-based Stratus EMS allows you to monitor data center facilities and environments with the same degree of certainty you\u2019ve come to expect from Sensaphone.\u00a0Users can check critical conditions of their climate and equipment-sensitive commodities at any time. The Stratus EMS monitors, delivers alarms, and data logs 64 input\/output points from Modbus inputs in addition to 12 universal digital or analog inputs.\u00a0It supports Modbus RTU\/485 and Modbus TCP which make is capable of reading data from many IDF, PDU, UPS and Building Automation Systems. It takes the burden out of managing your system by giving you access to your readings from anywhere using a simple, powerful web-based interface. If there\u2019s a disruption, you\u2019ll be the first to know. Alerts can be sent straight to your mobile device\u2014keeping you updated and giving you peace-of-mind wherever you are so you can remain focused on business as usual.\u003C\/p\u003E\n\u003Cul\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EINCLUDED\u003C\/strong\u003E: Internal rechargeable battery-backup system will provide up to 30 hours of continuous monitoring and alerting in the event of a power outage.\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EINCLUDED\u003C\/strong\u003E: Power failure monitoring\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003C\/ul\u003E\u003Ch3\u003ETechnical Specifications\u003C\/h3\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\"vouter\"\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\"vcenter col-1\"\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ECommunication Method:\u003C\/strong\u003E\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\"vcenter col-2\"\u003EEthernet\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\"vouter\"\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\"vcenter col-1\"\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ENumber of Inputs:\u003C\/strong\u003E\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\"vcenter col-2\"\u003E12 Digital or Analog &amp; 64 Modbus Registers\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\"vouter\"\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\"vcenter col-1\"\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EInput Types:\u003C\/strong\u003E\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\"vcenter col-2\"\u003EModbus, 2.8K, 10K, Dry Contact, 4-20mA,\u00a0\u003Cbr\u003E24V power for current loops\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\"vouter\"\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\"vcenter col-1\"\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EOutput Relay:\u003C\/strong\u003E\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\"vcenter col-2\"\u003ETwo low voltage NO\/NC relay output\u003Cbr\u003EManual or automatic alarm switching\u003Cbr\u003E12V power for current loops\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\"vouter\"\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\"vcenter col-1\"\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ETemperature Sensing Range:\u003C\/strong\u003E\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\"vcenter col-2\"\u003E-109\u00b0 to 168\u00b0F | -85\u00b0 to 76\u00b0C\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\"vouter\"\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\"vcenter col-1\"\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ERemote Access:\u003C\/strong\u003E\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\"vcenter col-2\"\u003EWebsite and mobile app to access status and programming\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\"vouter\"\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\"vcenter col-1\"\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ELocal Access:\u003C\/strong\u003E\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\"vcenter col-2\"\u003ELEDs for Alarm Status, Power Status, and Ethernet link\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\"vouter\"\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\"vcenter col-1\"\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EAlarm Notification:\u003C\/strong\u003E\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\"vcenter col-2\"\u003EAn unlimited number of email, text or phone calls\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\"vouter\"\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\"vcenter col-1\"\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EData Logging:\u003C\/strong\u003E\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\"vcenter col-2\"\u003EUnlimited samples securely stored on the Sentinel servers\u003Cbr\u003EProgrammable sampling Interval - 5 mins to 24 hrs\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\"vouter\"\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\"vcenter col-1\"\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EBattery Backup Time:\u003C\/strong\u003E\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\"vcenter col-2\"\u003EUp to 30 hours of battery backup time\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\"vouter\"\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\"vcenter col-1\"\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EPower Supply:\u003C\/strong\u003E\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\"vcenter col-2\"\u003EStratus EMS: 90-214VAC\/12VAC 50\/60Hz 30W plug-in transformer w\/ cord\u003Cbr\u003EBuilt in battery backup\u00a0\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EIntegrated Power Supply\u003C\/strong\u003E:\u003Cbr\u003EEach zone can supply 24VDC up to 50mA for current transducers \u003C\/span\u003E\n\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\"vouter\"\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\"vcenter col-1\"\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EPhysical\u003C\/strong\u003E\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\"vcenter col-2\"\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EStratus EMS:\u003C\/strong\u003E\u003Cbr\u003EWithout Mounting Ears: 17.6 x 7.9 x 1.7\" | 47 x 200 x 43mm\u003Cbr\u003EWith Mounting Ears: 18.8 x 7.9 x 1.7\" | 477 x 200 x 43mm\u003Cbr\u003E6lbs | 2.7kg\u00a0\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\"vouter\"\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\"vcenter col-1\"\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ERack Mount Size:\u003C\/strong\u003E\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\"vcenter col-2\"\u003E1U rackmount\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\"vouter\"\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\"vcenter col-1\"\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EAPI Data Interchange Formats:\u003C\/strong\u003E\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\"vcenter col-2\"\u003EJSON, HTTPS, POST, REST web services, cURL\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\"vouter\"\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\"vcenter col-1\"\u003EModbus\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\"vcenter col-2\"\u003ERS485 and TCP\/IP\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\"vouter\"\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\"vcenter col-1\"\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EWarranty:\u003C\/strong\u003E\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\"vcenter col-2\"\u003E3 years\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\"vcenter col-2\"\u003E\u00a0\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003Ch3 class=\"vcenter col-2\"\u003EDownloads\u003C\/h3\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\"vcenter col-2\"\u003E\u003Ca href=\"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1