[2026-02-18 07:41:58] [INFO] Product variant images has been updated - Shopidy ID - 10201312821562 - BC id=121 => {"product":{"id":10201312821562,"title":"Sensaphone 400 & 800 Monitoring Systems","body_html":"\u003Ch3\u003EAuto Dialer Temperature Alarm Provides Instant Notifications\u003C\/h3\u003E\n\u003Cul\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003ESimple, convenient, cost-effective remote monitoring for vacation homes and property managers\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003ERecord custom voice alerts and receive alarm messages in your own voice\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003EReceive voice alerts and alarm notifications over standard telephone lines\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003ENotifies up to four people by voice phone call in the event of an alarm\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003EUp to four or eight external sensors monitor temperature, humidity, water, and more\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003EIncluded relay output can switch local devices on\/off based on alarm activity\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003ETemperature-sensing range of -20\u00b0 to 150\u00b0F | -30\u00b0 to 65\u00b0C\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003EUse a dual setback thermostat to control temperature between two set points\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003EMade in USA\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003C\/ul\u003E\u003Cp class=\"BasicParagraph\"\u003EThe \u003Cstrong\u003ESensaphone 400 &amp; 800 Monitoring Systems\u003C\/strong\u003E offer small-business owners, vacation property owners, and other property managers an easy and inexpensive way to monitor a remote facility. Commonly referred to as an auto dialer, this \u00a0system will notify you if it senses undesirable temperatures or other conditions.\u003C\/p\u003E\n\u003Cp class=\"BasicParagraph\"\u003EWhen the system is connected to a standard telephone line, you can record custom \u201cAlert Condition\u201d notifications and receive alarm messages in your own voice. This system can set off a local alarm if a phone line is cut and control a thermostat to adjust site temperature between two set points. Nonvolatile memory retains system settings in the event of power loss. You can call in by phone to get the status of each monitored condition.\u003C\/p\u003E\n\u003Cul\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cspan lang=\"en-US\"\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EINCLUDED:\u003C\/strong\u003E\u003C\/span\u003E\u003Cspan lang=\"en-US\"\u003E Internal battery backup system provides 24 hours of continuous monitoring and alerts in the event of a power outage\u003Cbr\u003E\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cspan lang=\"en-US\"\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EINCLUDED:\u003C\/strong\u003E\u003C\/span\u003E\u003Cspan lang=\"en-US\"\u003E A pre-installed temperature probe to monitor conditions at the installation location\u003Cbr\u003E\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cspan lang=\"en-US\"\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ENO MONTHLY FEES:\u003C\/strong\u003E\u003C\/span\u003E\u003Cspan lang=\"en-US\"\u003E unlike other systems that require ongoing expenses\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003C\/ul\u003E\u003Ch3\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cspan lang=\"en-US\"\u003ETechnical Specifications\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/h3\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\"vouter\"\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\"vcenter col-1\"\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ECommunication Method:\u003C\/strong\u003E\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\"vcenter col-2\"\u003EPhone Line\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\"vouter\"\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\"vcenter col-1\"\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ENumber of Inputs:\u003C\/strong\u003E\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\"vcenter col-2\"\u003E4 or 8\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\"vouter\"\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\"vcenter col-1\"\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EInput Types:\u003C\/strong\u003E\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\"vcenter col-2\"\u003EContact &amp; 2.8K\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\"vouter\"\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\"vcenter col-1\"\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ETemperature Sensing Range:\u003C\/strong\u003E\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\"vcenter col-2\"\u003E-20\u00b0 to 150\u00b0F | -30\u00b0 to 65\u00b0C\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\"vouter\"\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\"vcenter col-1\"\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EOutput Relay:\u003C\/strong\u003E\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\"vcenter col-2\"\u003EOne low voltage NO\/NC relay output\u003Cbr\u003EManual or automatic alarm switching\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\"vouter\"\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\"vcenter col-1\"\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ERemote Access:\u003C\/strong\u003E\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\"vcenter col-2\"\u003ECall in to check status and make programming changes\u003Cbr\u003EMicrophone for listen in status\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\"vouter\"\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\"vcenter col-1\"\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ELocal Access:\u003C\/strong\u003E\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\"vcenter col-2\"\u003EKeypad and speaker for local programming\u003Cbr\u003EEasy voice prompted programming\u003Cbr\u003EPassword Protected\u003Cbr\u003ELEDs\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\"vouter\"\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\"vcenter col-1\"\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EAlarm Notification:\u003C\/strong\u003E\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\"vcenter col-2\"\u003EThe Sensaphone 400 provides four custom voice phone calls\u003Cbr\u003EThe Sensaphone 800 provides eight custom voice phone calls\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\"vouter\"\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\"vcenter col-1\"\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EPower Supply:\u003C\/strong\u003E\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\"vcenter col-2\"\u003EPlug in power supply also monitors for power failures\u003Cbr\u003EInternal battery backup (requires 6 'C' cell batteries)\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\"vouter\"\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\"vcenter col-1\"\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EPhysical:\u003C\/strong\u003E\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\"vcenter col-2\"\u003E2.1 x 7.8 x 8.8\" | 53 x 198 x 223mm\u003Cbr\u003E2lbs | .9kg\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\"vouter\"\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\"vcenter col-1\"\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EEnclosure:\u003C\/strong\u003E\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\"vcenter col-2\"\u003EIndoor-rated plastic housing suitable for wall or desktop installation.\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\"vouter\"\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\"vcenter col-1\"\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EWarranty:\u003C\/strong\u003E\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\"vcenter col-2\"\u003E1 Year\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\"vouter\"\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\"vcenter col-1\"\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EStandards:\u003C\/strong\u003E\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\"vcenter col-2\"\u003EFCC Part 15 Class B, USA Emission Standards\u003Cbr\u003EFCC Part 68 (47 C.F.R. Part 68), USA Telecommunications Standards\u003Cbr\u003EICES-003 Issue 4 Class B, Canadian Emission Standards\u003Cbr\u003EComplies with CS-03 Issue 8, Canadian Telecommunications Standards\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cspan\u003ENRTL Listed for compliance to UL\/CSA 62368-1 Safety Standards\u003C\/span\u003E\u003Cbr\u003ERoHS Compliant\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\"vouter\"\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\"vcenter col-1\"\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EBattery Backup Time:\u003C\/strong\u003E\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\"vcenter col-2\"\u003E24 hours\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003Ch3\u003EDownloads\u003C\/h3\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\u003Ca href=\"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0987\/4738\/4122\/files\/LIT-0129_400_Manual_v1.5.9_WEB.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"\u003ESensaphone 400 Monitoring System User's Manual\u003C\/a\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Ca href=\"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0987\/4738\/4122\/files\/LIT-0130_800_Manualv1.7.1_WEB.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopen