[2026-02-18 07:43:57] [INFO] Product variant images has been updated - Shopidy ID - 10201313509690 - BC id=126 => {"product":{"id":10201313509690,"title":"Sensaphone WSG30 Monitoring System","body_html":"\u003Ch3\u003EWireless, Web-Based Monitoring and Data Logging... Made Easy\u003C\/h3\u003E\n\u003Cul\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003EAn easy solution to web-based monitoring and ideal for applications where running wires can be difficult\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003EReceive alarm notifications through a standard Ethernet connection\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003ENotifies up to 32 people by email, email-to-text message, SNMP, or Modbus in the event of an alarm\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003EUp to 30 external wireless sensors monitor temperature, humidity, water, and more\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003ENative temperature sensing range of -109\u00b0 to 115\u00b0F | -85\u00b0 to 57\u00b0C\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003EExtended temperature ranges from -328\u00b0 to 248\u00b0F | -200\u00b0 to 120\u00b0C available\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003EData logger records up to 67,000 samples, including data, date, and time\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003EMake programming changes and access status conditions online\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003EMade in the USA\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003C\/ul\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan\u003EThe \u003C\/span\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ESensaphone WSG30 Monitoring System\u003C\/strong\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E offers a flexible monitoring solution when hard-wiring sensors is not a cost-effective or viable option. It also functions as a data logger to demonstrate compliance. The \u003C\/span\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EWSG30\u003C\/strong\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E is encased in a stylish, wall-mountable enclosure with an easy-to-read, 80-character LCD display. A built-in rechargeable battery backup, data logging, and a standard temperature sensing range (-109\u00b0 to 115\u00b0F) make this unit an excellent choice for any wireless application. A \u003C\/span\u003E\u003Ca href=\"%%GLOBAL_ShopPathSSL%%\/products\/WSG-Wireless-Temperature-Sensor-with-RTD-Probe\"\u003Ewireless temperature sensor with an RTD probe\u003C\/a\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E is also available for measuring extreme air temperature from\u00a0\u003C\/span\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E-328\u00b0 to 248\u00b0F | -200\u00b0 to 120\u00b0C.\u00a0\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/p\u003E\n\u003Cul\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cspan lang=\"en-US\"\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EINCLUDED:\u003C\/strong\u003E\u003C\/span\u003E\u003Cspan lang=\"en-US\"\u003E Internal rechargeable battery-backup system provides two hours of continuous monitoring and alerts in the event of a power outage\u003Cbr\u003E\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cspan lang=\"en-US\"\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EINCLUDED:\u003C\/strong\u003E\u003C\/span\u003E\u003Cspan lang=\"en-US\"\u003E Power failure monitoring\u00a0\u003Cbr\u003E\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cspan lang=\"en-US\"\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ENO MONTHLY FEES:\u003C\/strong\u003E\u003C\/span\u003E\u003Cspan lang=\"en-US\"\u003E Unlike other systems that require subscriptions\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003C\/ul\u003E\u003Ch3\u003ETechnical Specifications\u003C\/h3\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\"vouter\"\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\"vcenter col-1\"\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ECommunication Method:\u003C\/strong\u003E\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\"vcenter col-2\"\u003EEthernet\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\"vouter\"\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\"vcenter col-1\"\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ENumber of Inputs:\u003C\/strong\u003E\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\"vcenter col-2\"\u003E30 Wireless Sensors\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\"vcenter col-2\"\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EInput Types:\u003C\/strong\u003E\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\"vouter\"\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\"vcenter col-2\"\u003E\u003Cspan\u003EWSG30 Wireless (Temperature, Humidity, Dry Contact, 4-20mA, Water Detection, Power Failure)\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\"vouter\"\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\"vcenter col-1\"\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ETemperature Sensing Range:\u003C\/strong\u003E\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\"vcenter col-2\"\u003E-109\u00b0 to 115\u00b0F | -85\u00b0 to 57\u00b0C (standard)\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E-328\u00b0 to 248\u00b0F | -200\u00b0 to 120\u00b0C (with RTD Sensor)\u003C\/span\u003E\n\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\"vouter\"\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\"vcenter col-1\"\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ERemote Access:\u003C\/strong\u003E\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\"vcenter col-2\"\u003EWebsite to access status and programming\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\"vouter\"\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\"vcenter col-1\"\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ELocal Access:\u003C\/strong\u003E\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\"vcenter col-2\"\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E4 line LCD display and keypad\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\"vouter\"\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\"vcenter col-1\"\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EAlarm Notification:\u003C\/strong\u003E\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\"vcenter col-2\"\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E32 e-mail and\/or email-to-text messages, SNMP trap, Modbus\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\"vouter\"\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\"vcenter col-1\"\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EPower Supply:\u003C\/strong\u003E\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\"vcenter col-2\"\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003EPlug in power supply also monitors for power failures \u003C\/span\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cspan\u003EInternal battery backup\u003C\/span\u003E\n\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\"vouter\"\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\"vcenter col-1\"\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EBattery Backup Time:\u003C\/strong\u003E\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\"vcenter col-1\"\u003E2 hours\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\"vcenter col-1\"\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EData Logging:\u003C\/strong\u003E\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\"vcenter col-2\"\u003E67,000 samples (include data, date and time)\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\"vouter\"\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\"vcenter col-1\"\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EPhysical:\u003C\/strong\u003E\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\"vcenter col-2\"\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003E7.4 x 5.1 x 2\" | 190 x 130 x 50mm \u003C\/span\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E2.5lbs | 1.3kg\u003C\/span\u003E\n\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\"vouter\"\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\"vcenter col-1\"\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EWarranty:\u003C\/strong\u003E\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\"vcenter col-2\"\u003E1 Year\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\"vcenter col-2\"\u003E\u00a0\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\"vcenter col-2\"\u003EDownloads:\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\"vcenter col-2\"\u003E\u003Ca href=\"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0987\/4738\/4122\/files\/1ce60a42515f183cd0d3feddb8da165f.mib\"\u003ESensaphone WSG30 SNMP MIB\u003C\/a\u003E\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\"vcenter col-2\"\u003E\u003Ca href=\"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0987\/4738\/4122\/files\/SensaphoneLocator.exe\"\u003ESensaphone WSG30 Locator Software\u003C\/a\u003E\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\"vcenter col-2\"\u003E\u003Ca href=\"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0987\/4738\/4122\/files\/WSG30Firmware.bin\"\u003ESensaphone WSG30 Firmware Download\u003C\/a\u003E\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\"vcenter col-2\"\u003E\u003Ca href=\"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0987\/4738\/4122\/files\/LIT-1029_WSG30_Brochure.pdf\"\u003ESensaphone WSG30 Sales Brochure\u003C\/a\u003E\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\"vcenter col-2\"\u003E\u003Ca href=\"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0987\/4738\/4122\/files\/WSG30_TechSpecs.pdf\"\u003ESensaphone WSG30 Technical Specifications\u003C\/a\