[2026-02-18 07:44:43] [INFO] Product variant images has been updated - Shopidy ID - 10201313804602 - BC id=129 => {"product":{"id":10201313804602,"title":"Sensaphone 1400 & 1800 Monitoring Systems","body_html":"\u003Cdiv class=\"simple-tabs-content entry-content\"\u003E\n\u003Ch3\u003EAlarm Auto Dialer Ensures 24\/7 Monitoring\u003C\/h3\u003E\n\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003Cul\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003ESimple, convenient, cost-effective remote monitoring ideal for greenhouse and agriculture applications\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003ERugged, weatherproof NEMA-4X enclosure offers protection in harsh environments\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003EReceive voice alerts and alarm notifications over standard telephone lines\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003EAuto dialer: Notifies up to eight people by voice phone call in the event of an alarm\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003EUp to eight external sensors monitor temperature, humidity, water and more\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003EIncluded relay output can switch local devices on\/off based on alarm activity\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003ETemperature-sensing range of -109\u00b0 to -168\u00b0F | -85\u00b0 to -76\u00b0C\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003ERecord custom voice alerts and receive alarm messages in your own voice\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003EMade in USA\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003C\/ul\u003E\u003Cp\u003EThe \u003Cstrong\u003ESensaphone 1400 &amp; 1800 Monitoring Systems\u003C\/strong\u003E offer an easy and inexpensive way to monitor up to eight inputs under the harshest conditions. Commonly called auto dialers, these systems notify you if they sense undesirable temperatures or other conditions. You can record custom alerts and receive alarm messages in your own voice.\u003C\/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003EIn addition to dry contact, 2.8K, and 10K thermistor inputs, 4-20mA support allows for third-party sensor integration. Nonvolatile memory retains system settings, programming, and even logs in the event of power failure. You can call in by phone to get the status of each monitored condition.\u003C\/p\u003E\n\u003Cul\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cspan lang=\"en-US\"\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EINCLUDED:\u003C\/strong\u003E\u003C\/span\u003E\u003Cspan lang=\"en-US\"\u003E Internal battery backup system provides 24 hours of continuous monitoring and alerts in the event of a power outage\u003Cbr\u003E\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cspan lang=\"en-US\"\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EINCLUDED:\u003C\/strong\u003E\u003C\/span\u003E\u003Cspan lang=\"en-US\"\u003E One weatherproof temperature sensor\u003Cbr\u003E\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cspan lang=\"en-US\"\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EINCLUDED:\u003C\/strong\u003E\u003C\/span\u003E\u003Cspan lang=\"en-US\"\u003E Power failure monitoring\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/span\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cspan lang=\"en-US\"\u003E\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/span\u003E\n\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cspan lang=\"en-US\"\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ENO MONTHLY FEES:\u003C\/strong\u003E\u003C\/span\u003E\u003Cspan lang=\"en-US\"\u003E unlike other systems that require subscriptions\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003C\/ul\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u00a0\u003C\/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\"vouter\"\u003E\n\u003Ch3 class=\"vcenter col-1\"\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ETech Specs\u003C\/strong\u003E\u003C\/h3\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\"vcenter col-1\"\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ECommunication Method:\u003C\/strong\u003E\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\"vcenter col-2\"\u003EPhone Line\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\"vouter\"\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\"vcenter col-1\"\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ENumber of Inputs:\u003C\/strong\u003E\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\"vcenter col-2\"\u003E4 or 8\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\"vouter\"\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\"vcenter col-1\"\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EInput Types:\u003C\/strong\u003E\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\"vcenter col-2\"\u003EContact, 2.8k, 10k , 4-20mA\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\"vouter\"\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\"vcenter col-1\"\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ETemperature Sensing Range:\u003C\/strong\u003E\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\"vcenter col-2\"\u003E-109\u00b0 to 168\u00b0F | -85\u00b0 to 76\u00b0C\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\"vouter\"\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\"vcenter col-1\"\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EOutput Relay:\u003C\/strong\u003E\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\"vcenter col-2\"\u003EOne universal input relay\u003Cbr\u003EManual or automatic alarm switching\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\"vouter\"\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\"vcenter col-1\"\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ERemote Access:\u003C\/strong\u003E\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\"vcenter col-2\"\u003ECall in to check status and make programming changes\u003Cbr\u003EMicrophone for listen in status\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\"vouter\"\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\"vcenter col-1\"\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ELocal Access:\u003C\/strong\u003E\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\"vcenter col-2\"\u003EKeypad and speaker for local programming\u00a0\u003Cbr\u003EEasy voice prompted programming\u00a0\u003Cbr\u003EPassword Protected\u003Cbr\u003ERecent alarm history playback\u003Cbr\u003ELEDs\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\"vouter\"\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\"vcenter col-1\"\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EAlarm Notification:\u003C\/strong\u003E\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\"vcenter col-2\"\u003EEight custom voice phone calls\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\"vouter\"\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\"vcenter col-1\"\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EPower Supply:\u003C\/strong\u003E\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\"vcenter col-2\"\u003EPlug in power supply also monitors for power failures\u003Cbr\u003EInternal battery backup\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003C\/di