[2026-02-18 07:44:57] [INFO] Product variant images has been updated - Shopidy ID - 10201313870138 - BC id=130 => {"product":{"id":10201313870138,"title":"Contact Type Infrared Motion Detection Sensor","body_html":"\u003Ch3\u003EMonitor for the movement of warm bodies\u003C\/h3\u003E\n\u003Cul\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003EDetection range is up to 40 feet of area\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003EWhite plastic construction\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003EMultiple sensors can be wired into one Sensaphone input\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003C\/ul\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan\u003EThe Infrared Motion Detection Sensor can be used with all Sensaphone models to monitor the movement of warm bodies in a specific area. When a person enters the room, the sensor will trigger the Sensaphone to go into alarm. The range is a maximum of 40 feet directly ahead of, and approximately 20 feet to either side of, the detector at 40 feet distance. \u003C\/span\u003E\u003Cspan\u003EThe sensor requires 12VDC power (included) for operation\u003C\/span\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E\u00a0and mounts to the wall the included hardware. The sensor is connected to the Sensaphone via accessory wire (not included).\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E\u003C!-- pagebreak --\u003E\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/p\u003E\n\u003Ch3\u003E\u003Cspan\u003ETechnical Specifications\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/h3\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EConnection:\u003C\/strong\u003E Hardwired\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EHousing:\u003C\/strong\u003E White Plastic\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EDimensions:\u003C\/strong\u003E 3.4 x 2.2 x 1.7\" | 86 x 57 x 44mm\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EWeight:\u003C\/strong\u003E 2.15oz. | 61g\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ESensor Series:\u003C\/strong\u003E Contact Series\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EWall Mounting Height:\u003C\/strong\u003E 69 to 89\" (2.1 - 2.7 m); Optimal 76\" (2.3 m)\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ERange:\u003C\/strong\u003E Approximately 40'\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EOperating Temperature:\u003C\/strong\u003E 14\u00b0 to 131\u00b0F | -10\u00b0 to 55\u00b0C\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EApproval Listings:\u003C\/strong\u003E FCC part 15, Class B verified, IC ICES-003, Class B verified, ETL Listed to UL 639\u003Cbr\u003E\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/p\u003E\n\u003Ch3\u003E\u003Cspan\u003EDownloads\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/h3\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E\u003Ca href=\"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0987\/4738\/4122\/files\/FGD_0007-HW_CS.pdf\"\u003EContact Type Infrared Motion Detection Sensor Sales Brochure\u003C\/a\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Ca href=\"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0987\/4738\/4122\/files\/LIT-0093_InfraredMotion_Instructions.pdf\"\u003EContact Type Infrared Motion Detection Sensor Instructions\u003C\/a\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/p\u003E","vendor":"Sensaphone","product_type":"physical","created_at":"2026-02-18T01:44:55-05:00","handle":"contact-type-infrared-motion-detection-sensor","updated_at":"2026-02-18T01:44:55-05:00","published_at":"2026-02-18T01:44:49-05:00","template_suffix":null,"published_scope":"global","tags":"BRAND__Sensaphone, CAT__Security__VAL, MAINSKU__FGD-0007-HW, OLD__130__ID, TYPE__physical","status":"active","admin_graphql_api_id":"gid:\/\/shopify\/Product\/10201313870138","variants":[{"id":53038655439162,"product_id":10201313870138,"title":"Default Title","price":"79.00","position":1,"inventory_policy":"continue","compare_at_price":null,"option1":"Default Title","option2":null,"option3":null,"created_at":"2026-02-18T01:44:55-05:00","updated_at":"2026-02-18T01:44:56-05:00","taxable":true,"barcode":"","fulfillment_service":"manual","grams":59,"inventory_management":"shopify","requires_shipping":true,"sku":"FGD-0007-HW","weight":0.13000000000000000444089209850062616169452667236328125,"weight_unit":"lb","inventory_item_id":55065759646010,"inventory_quantity":0,"old_inventory_quantity":0,"admin_graphql_api_id":"gid:\/\/shopify\/Pr