[2026-02-18 07:45:21] [INFO] Product variant images has been updated - Shopidy ID - 10201314099514 - BC id=134 => {"product":{"id":10201314099514,"title":"Contact Type Temp Alert Temperature Switch","body_html":"\u003Ch3\u003EMonitor air temperature from 20\u00b0 to 110\u00b0F | 6.7\u00b0 to 43.3\u00b0C\u003C\/h3\u003E\n\u003Cul\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003EMonitors temperatures from 20\u00b0 to 110\u00b0F | 6.7\u00b0 to 43.3\u00b0C\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003ESends a simple alarm or no alarm status to the Sensaphone\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003EProvides a local display of temperature reading\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003EMultiple sensors can be added to one Sensaphone input\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003ESeparate output for high and low alarm signals\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003ENo power required to operate\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E1 year warranty\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003C\/ul\u003E\u003Cp\u003EThe Temp Alert Temperature Switch can be used with all Sensaphone models. It monitors air temperature from 20\u00b0 to 110\u00b0F | 6.7\u00b0 to 43.3\u00b0C. By adjusting the temperature limit arms, you can select the acceptable temperature limits for your application. Simply use a screwdriver to set the temperature limit arms on the rear of the device.\u003C\/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003EWhen the ambient air temperature rises or falls to the limit arms, the temperature sensor triggers an alarm. The\u00a0temperature alert can be mounted to any wall or vertical surface. Multiple temp alerts may be wired in parallel to a single input. It requires no power for operation and mounts easily on any flat surface.\u003C\/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\u003C!-- pagebreak --\u003E\u003C\/p\u003E\n\u003Ch3\u003ETechnical Specifications\u003C\/h3\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ESensor Temperature Range:\u003C\/strong\u003E Alarm Use: 20\u00b0 to 110\u00b0F (6.7\u00b0 to 43.3\u00b0C) | Display use: 0\u00b0 to 120\u00b0F (-17.8\u00b0 to 48.9\u00b0C)\u00a0\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EAccuracy:\u003C\/strong\u003E 3\u00b0F | 1.7\u00b0C\u00a0\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EConnection:\u003C\/strong\u003E Hardwired\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EHousing:\u003C\/strong\u003E Plastic\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EDimensions:\u003C\/strong\u003E 4.5 x 3.25 x 1\" | 11.4 x 8.3 x 2.5cm\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ESensor Series:\u003C\/strong\u003E Contact Series\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ETemp Response Time:\u003C\/strong\u003E TC = 14 minutes\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EMinimum Temp Span:\u003C\/strong\u003E 10 Recommended distance between high and low set points\u003C\/p\u003E\n\u003Ch3\u003EDownloads\u003C\/h3\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\u003Ca href=\"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0987\/4738\/4122\/files\/FGD-0022_CS.pdf\"\u003EContact Type Temp Alert Temperature Switch Sales Brochure\u003C\/a\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Ca href=\"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0987\/4738\/4122\/files\/LIT-0096_TempAlert_Instructions.pdf\"\u003EContact Type Temp Alert Temperature Switch Instructions\u003C\/a\u003E\u003C\/p\u003E","vendor":"Sensaphone","product_type":"physical","created_at":"2026-02-18T01:45:19-05:00","handle":"contact-type-temp-alert-temperature-switch","updated_at":"2026-02-18T01:45:20-05:00","published_at":"2026-02-18T01:45:15-05:00","template_suffix":null,"published_scope":"global","tags":"BRAND__Sensaphone, CAT__Temperature Sensors__VAL, MAINSKU__FGD-0022, OLD__134__ID, TYPE__physical","status":"active","admin_graphql_api_id":"gid:\/\/shopify\/Product\/10201314099514","variants":[{"id":53038656454970,"product_id":10201314099514,"title":"Default Title","price":"99.00","position":1,"inventory_policy":"continue","compare_at_price":null,"option1":"Default Title","option2":null,"option3":null,"created_at":"2026-02-18T01:45:20-05:00","updated_at":"2026-02-18T01:45:20-05:00","taxable":true,"barcode":"","fulfillment_service":"manual","grams":0,"inventory_management":"shopify","requires_shipping":true,"sku":"FGD-0022","weight":0,"weight_unit":"l