[2026-02-18 07:45:30] [INFO] Product variant images has been updated - Shopidy ID - 10201314132282 - BC id=135 => {"product":{"id":10201314132282,"title":"Contact Type Humidistat Humidity Switch","body_html":"\u003Ch3\u003EDetect high or low humidity\u003C\/h3\u003E\n\u003Cul\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003EMonitors humidity ranges from 20% to 80%\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003EAlarm values are set on the sensor\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003ESensor provides simple alarm or no alarm status to Sensaphone\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003EReceive alerts from your Sensaphone when the status changes\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003C\/ul\u003E\u003Cp style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003EThe Humidistat Humidity Switch is a hard-wired humidity sensor that can be used with all Sensaphone models to detect high or low humidity levels. Users set a high or low alarm limit by adjusting the dial on the front of the sensor. When that limit is exceeded, the device will trip an alarm to the Sensaphone.\u003C\/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003EMade from high impact white plastic, a nylon sensing element provides long life and accurate humidity control. The sensor has a range of 20% to 80% relative humidity. Multiple sensors may be wired to a single input. The humidistat switch can be installed in any location, home or office, and will work accurately for many years.\u003C\/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003E\u003C!-- pagebreak --\u003E\u003C\/p\u003E\n\u003Ch3\u003ETechnical Specifications\u003C\/h3\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EOperating Temperature:\u003C\/strong\u003E 32\u00b0 to 95\u00b0F | -0\u00b0 to 35\u00b0C\u00a0\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EHumidity Range:\u003C\/strong\u003E 20% to 80%\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EConnection:\u003C\/strong\u003E Hardwired\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EHousing:\u003C\/strong\u003E Plastic\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EDimensions:\u003C\/strong\u003E 4.5 x 3 x 1.7\" | 114 x 76 x 43mm\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ESensor Series:\u003C\/strong\u003E Contact Series\u003C\/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003EDownloads\u003C\/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003E\u003Ca href=\"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0987\/4738\/4122\/files\/FGD-0027_CS.pdf\"\u003EContact Type Humidistat Humidity Switch Sales Brochure\u003C\/a\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Ca href=\"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0987\/4738\/4122\/files\/LIT-0080_Humidistat_Instructionv3.0.pdf\"\u003EContact Type Humidistat Humidity Switch Instructions\u003C\/a\u003E\u003C\/p\u003E","vendor":"Sensaphone","product_type":"physical","created_at":"2026-02-18T01:45:28-05:00","handle":"contact-type-humidistat-humidity-switch","updated_at":"2026-02-18T01:45:29-05:00","published_at":"2026-02-18T01:45:26-05:00","template_suffix":null,"published_scope":"global","tags":"BRAND__Sensaphone, CAT__Humidity Sensors__VAL, MAINSKU__FGD-0027, OLD__135__ID, TYPE__physical","status":"active","admin_graphql_api_id":"gid:\/\/shopify\/Product\/10201314132282","variants":[{"id":53038656618810,"product_id":10201314132282,"title":"Default Title","price":"55.00","position":1,"inventory_policy":"continue","compare_at_price":null,"option1":"Default Title","option2":null,"option3":null,"created_at":"2026-02-18T01:45:28-05:00","updated_at":"2026-02-18T01:45:29-05:00","taxable":true,"barcode":"","fulfillment_service":"manual","grams":0,"inventory_management":"shopify","requires_shipping":true,"sku":"FGD-0027","weight":0,"weight_unit":"lb","inventory_item_id":55065760825658,"inventory_quantity":0,"old_inventory_quantity":0,"admin_graphql_api_id":"gid:\/\/shopify\/ProductVariant\/53038656618810","image_id":null}],"options":[{"id":12742205800762,"product_id":10201314132282,"name":"Title","position":1,"values":["Default Title"]}],"images":[{"id":55073490895162,"alt":"135_main_image_0","position":1,"product_id":10201314132282,"created_at":"2026-02-18T01:45:28-05:00","updated_at":"2026-02-18T01:45:28-05:0