[2026-02-18 07:45:38] [INFO] Product variant images has been updated - Shopidy ID - 10201314197818 - BC id=136 => {"product":{"id":10201314197818,"title":"Contact Type Smoke Detector Sensor","body_html":"\u003Ch3\u003ESmoke Detection\u003C\/h3\u003E\n\u003Cul\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003EMulti-Criteria smoke sensing including photoelectric light scattering sensing technology\u00a0\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E10-year end-of-life indicator\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003ETemporal 3 evacuation signal pattern for smoke and heat annunciation\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E85 dBA evacuation horn piezo\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003EHorn frequency 3100Hz\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003ENominal 2.5% sensitivity\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E8-hour alarm memory\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003EPush button self-test\u00a0\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003EPush button functional test\u00a0\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003EQuick-disconnect wiring harness\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003ENon-latching (self restoring) alarm\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003EPulsing LED sensing chamber\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003EFully insect screened\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003EMounting hardware adapts to standard junction boxes\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003EDust cover to prevent contamination during installation\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003ELow or missing battery indicator\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003EConnect up to twelve smoke detector sensors to one Sensaphone input\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003C\/ul\u003E\u003Cp\u003EThe Smoke Detector is designed for use in commercial and residential applications and is engineered to virtually eliminate nuisance alarms and deliver outstanding performance wherever reliable smoke detection is required. Up to 12 devices can be connected together and report to one Sensaphone zone. A 85 dBA audible horn and 9V battery backup is included. This smoke detector can be used with all Sensaphone models.\u003C\/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E\u003C!-- pagebreak --\u003E\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/p\u003E\n\u003Ch3\u003E\u003Cspan\u003ETechnical Specifications\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/h3\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EOperating Temperature:\u003C\/strong\u003E 40\u00b0 to 100\u00b0F | 4\u00b0 to 37\u00b0C\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EOperating Voltage:\u003C\/strong\u003E 120VAC, 60Hz\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EDimensions:\u003C\/strong\u003E 6.25 diameter x 1.8\" | 72mm x 40mm\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EOperating Current (Relay Options):\u003C\/strong\u003E 0.070 amps\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EAlarm Horn Rating:\u003C\/strong\u003E Meets or exceeds 85dBA at 10\u2019\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ENominal Sensitivity:\u003C\/strong\u003E 2.5% obscuration\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003E\u201cF\u201d Auxiliary Relay:\u003C\/strong\u003E 1 Form A and 1 Form C (0.6 amp)\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ESecondary Power Source:\u003C\/strong\u003E Alkaline 9V battery, Duracell\u00ae MN 1604\u003Cbr\u003E\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/p\u003E\n\u003Ch3\u003EDownloads\u003C\/h3\u003E\n\u003Cdiv\u003E\u003Ca href=\"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0987\/4738\/4122\/files\/FGD-0049-SQ_CS.pdf\"\u003ESensaphone Smoke Detector Cutsheet\u003C\/a\u003E\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv\u003E\u003Ca href=\"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0987\/4738\/4122\/files\/LIT-0098%20FGD-0049%20instructions.pdf\"\u003ESensaphone Smoke Detector Instructions\u003C\/a\u003E\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\u00a0\u003C\/p\u003E","vendor":"Sensaphone","product_type":"physical","created_at":"2026-02-18T01:45:37-05:00","handle":"contact-type-smoke-detector-sensor","updated_at":"2026-02-18T01:45:37-05:00","published_at":"2026-02-18T01:45:34-05:00","template_suffix":null,"published_scope":"global","tags":"BRAND__Sensaphone, CAT__Security__VAL, MAINSKU__FGD-0049-SQ, OLD__136__ID, TYPE__physical","status":"active","admin_graphql_api_id":"gid:\/\/shopify\/Product\/10201314197818","variants":[{"id":53038656979258,"product_id":10201314197818,"