[2026-02-18 07:45:49] [INFO] Product variant images has been updated - Shopidy ID - 10201314263354 - BC id=137 => {"product":{"id":10201314263354,"title":"4-20mA Type Humidity Sensor","body_html":"\u003Ch3\u003EMonitor Humidity Levels\u003C\/h3\u003E\n\u003Cul\u003E\n\u003Cli style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003EMeasures humidity from 0 to 95% RH\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003ESet high or low limit by programming the Sensaphone\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003ESensaphone will go into alarm when humidity exceeds limit\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003ERequires external power supply (FGD-0070)\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003C\/ul\u003E\u003Cp style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003EThe Sensaphone Humidity sensor will measure and provide real time humidity values to any Sensaphone that accepts a 4-20mA signal. When the humidity level falls outside of the Sensaphone\u2019s programmed high or low limit, the user will receive an alarm which displays or reads the current humidity value. The sensor can be programed to detect humidity levels from 0 to 95% RH. The low profile enclosure allows the sensor to be placed in a single gang electrical box or mounted directly to the wall. It is ideal for clean indoor applications such as a home, office, museum or hospital. A 24V DC power supply is required to power the sensor.\u003C\/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E\u003C!-- pagebreak --\u003E\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/p\u003E\n\u003Ch3\u003E\u003Cspan\u003ETechnical Specifications\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/h3\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EOperating Temperature:\u003C\/strong\u003E 35\u00b0 to 122\u00b0F | 1.5\u00b0 to 60\u00b0C\u00a0\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EHumidity:\u003C\/strong\u003E 0% to 95%\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EAccuracy:\u003C\/strong\u003E +\/-3% from 10 to 95%\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EConnection:\u003C\/strong\u003E Hardwired\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EHousing:\u0