[2026-02-18 07:46:39] [INFO] Product variant images has been updated - Shopidy ID - 10201314754874 - BC id=143 => {"product":{"id":10201314754874,"title":"Contact Type Zone Water Detection Sensor","body_html":"\u003Ch3\u003EWidespread water detection\u003C\/h3\u003E\n\u003Cul\u003E\n\u003Cli style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003EDetects water on a floor or false ceiling\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003ESends Sensaphone into alarm when water is detected\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003EIncludes 10\u2019 of water sensing rope\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003EUp to nine additional lengths of water rope can be added for expanding the water detection area\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003ECommon uses include: burst pipes that leak water, leaking AC unit, bad HVAC compressor, any water leak\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003C\/ul\u003E\u003Cp style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003EThe Zone Water Detection Sensor can be used with all Sensaphone models to monitor for the presence of water on a floor or in a false ceiling. When the included 10\u2019 water rope comes in contact with water, it will trigger the Sensaphone to go into alarm. This sensor is ideal for use in homes and businesses or anywhere that is susceptible to flooding. It operates on two AA batteries and when the batteries start to run down, the sensor will automatically send out an alarm. The sensor is connected to the Sensaphone via accessory wire (not included).\u003C\/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\u003C!-- pagebreak --\u003E\u003C\/p\u003E\n\u003Ch3\u003ETechnical Specifications\u003C\/h3\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EConnection:\u003C\/strong\u003E Hardwired\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EHousing:\u003C\/strong\u003E Plastic\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EDimensions:\u003C\/strong\u003E 5.5 x 3.3 x 1.4\" | 140 x 83 x 33mm\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ESensor Series: \u003C\/strong\u003EContact Series\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ENotes:\u003C\/strong\u003E Up to 10 water ropes can be cascaded from a single sensor\u003C\/p\u003E\n\u003Ch3\u003EDownloads\u003C\/h3\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\u003Ca href=\"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0987\/4738\/4122\/files\/FGD-0056_CS.pdf\"\u003EContact Type Zone Water Detection Sensor Sales Brochure\u003C\/a\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Ca href=\"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0987\/4738\/4122\/files\/LIT-0091_FGD-0056_Instructions.pdf\"\u003EContact Type Zone Water Detection Sensor Instructions\u003C\/a\u003E\u003C\/p\u003E","vendor":"Sensaphone","product_type":"physical","created_at":"2026-02-18T01:46:37-05:00","handle":"contact-type-zone-water-detection-sensor","updated_at":"2026-02-18T01:46:37-05:00","published_at":"2026-02-18T01:46:31-05:00","template_suffix":null,"published_scope":"global","tags":"BRAND__Sensaphone, CAT__Water Detection__VAL, MAINSKU__FGD-0056, OLD__143__ID, TYPE__physical","status":"active","admin_graphql_api_id":"gid:\/\/shopify\/Product\/10201314754874","variants":[{"id":53038659567930,"product_id":10201314754874,"title":"Default Title","price":"149.00","position":1,"inventory_policy":"continue","compare_at_price":null,"option1":"Default Title","option2":null,"option3":null,"created_at":"2026-02-18T01:46:37-05:00","updated_at":"2026-02-18T01:46:38-05:00","taxable":true,"barcode":"","fulfillment_service":"manual","grams":0,"inventory_management":"shopify","requires_shipping":true,"sku":"FGD-0056","weight":0,"weight_unit":"lb","inventory_item_id":55065763774778,"inventory_quantity":0,"old_inventory_quantity":0,"admin_graphql_api_id":"gid:\/\/shopify\/ProductVariant\/53038659567930","image_id":null}],"options":[{"id":12742206456122,"product_id":10201314754874,"name":"Title","position":1,"values":["Default Title"]}],"images":[{"id":55073495679290,"alt":"143_main_image_0","position":1,"product_id":10201314754874,"created_at":"2026-02-18T01:46:37-05:00","updated_at":"2026-02-18T01:46:37-05:00","admin_graphql_api_id":"gid:\/