[2026-02-18 07:47:00] [INFO] Product variant images has been updated - Shopidy ID - 10201314984250 - BC id=146 => {"product":{"id":10201314984250,"title":"Water Rope Extension for Zone Water Detectors","body_html":"\u003Ch3\u003EWidespread Water Detection\u003C\/h3\u003E\n\u003Cul\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003EExtends Water Detection Rope by 10 feet\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003EUp to 10 water ropes can be connected\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003ECompatible with the Zone Water Detector Sensor (#FGD-0056)\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003ECompatible with the Wireless Zone Water Sensor (#FGD-WSG30-ZONE)\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003ECommon uses include: burst pipes that leak water, leaking AC unit, bad HVAC compressor, any water leak\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003C\/ul\u003E\u003Cp style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003EThe Water Detection Rope can be used with Sensaphone Zone Water Detection Sensors to extend the sensor\u2019s ability to monitor for the presence of water on a floor or in a false ceiling. When the water rope comes in contact with water, it will trigger the Sensaphone to go into alarm. These water ropes can extend the sensor\u2019s ability from 10\u2019 to 100\u2019.\u003C\/p\u003E","vendor":"Sensaphone","product_type":"physical","created_at":"2026-02-18T01:46:59-05:00","handle":"water-rope-extension-for-zone-water-detectors","updated_at":"2026-02-18T01:46:59-05:00","published_at":"2026-02-18T01:46:56-05:00","template_suffix":null,"published_scope":"global","tags":"BRAND__Sensaphone, CAT__Water Detection__VAL, MAINSKU__FGD-0063, OLD__146__ID, TYPE__physical","status":"active","admin_graphql_api_id":"gid:\/\/shopify\/Product\/10201314984250","variants":[{"id":53038660419898,"product_id":10201314984250,"title":"Default Title","price":"90.00","position":1,"inventory_policy":"continue","compare_at_price":null,"option1":"Default Title","option2":null,"option3":null,"created_at":"2026-02-18T01:46:59-05:00","updated_at":"2026-02-18T01:46:59-05:00","taxable":true,"barcode":"","fulfil