[2026-02-18 07:47:14] [INFO] Product variant images has been updated - Shopidy ID - 10201315115322 - BC id=148 => {"product":{"id":10201315115322,"title":"Surge Suppressor for Power & Phone","body_html":"\u003Ch3\u003EPower surge protection\u003C\/h3\u003E\n\u003Cul\u003E\n\u003Cli style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003E\u003Cspan\u003ETravel size surge protector with a retractable plug \u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E(2) 120V outlets \u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E1-line (RJ11 jack) for telephone\/DSL modem\/fax protection - includes 6ft phone cord \u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E1050 joule surge suppression rating\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E120V only - not for international use\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003C\/ul\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003EThe Surge Suppressor can be used with all Sensaphone models to prevent power and phone line surges. T\u003C\/span\u003E\u003Cspan\u003Ehe retractable plug prevents scratching of expensive portable electronics when in transit. A set of two RJ11 telephone line suppression jacks protect dialup and voice\/modem lines. The suppressor offers two total 110V outlets in a space saving direct plug-in format and diagnostic LEDs to warn of problems.\u003C\/span\u003E\n\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E\u003C!-- pagebreak --\u003E\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/p\u003E\n\u003Ch3\u003E\u003Cspan\u003ETechnical Specifications\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/h3\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EVoltage Capacity:\u003C\/strong\u003E 120VAC\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EOutput Capacity:\u003C\/strong\u003E 15 Amps\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EAC Suppression Rating:\u003C\/strong\u003E 1,050 joules\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EDiagnostic LEDs:\u003C\/strong\u