[2026-02-18 07:47:26] [INFO] Product variant images has been updated - Shopidy ID - 10201315180858 - BC id=149 => {"product":{"id":10201315180858,"title":"4-20mA Type Carbon Dioxide (CO2) Sensor","body_html":"\u003Ch3\u003ECarbon Dioxide monitoring\u003C\/h3\u003E\n\u003Cul\u003E\n\u003Cli style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003EMeasures carbon dioxide from 0 to 2,000 PPM\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003EAccurate to \u00b130 PPM\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003ESet high and low limits by programming the Sensaphone\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003ESensaphone will go into alarm when carbon dioxide level exceeds limit\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003EHighly accurate and reliable Non-dispersive Infrared (NDIR) with state-of-the-art digital linearization and temperature compensated circuitry\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003C\/ul\u003E\u003Cp style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003EThe Sensaphone Carbon Dioxide Sensor will measure and provide real time carbon dioxide values to any Sensaphone that accepts a 4-20mA signal. When the carbon diooxide level falls outside of the Sensaphone\u2019s programmed high or low limit, the user will receive an alarm which displays or reads the current carbon dioxide value. The sensor can be programed to detect carbon diooxide levels from 0 to 2,000 PPM. The low profile enclosure allows the sensor to be mounted to a single gang electrical box or directly to a wall. A LCD displays the PPM and menu parameters. A 24V DC power supply is required to power the sensor.\u003C\/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\u003C!-- pagebreak --\u003E\u003C\/p\u003E\n\u003Ch3\u003ETechnical Specifications\u003C\/h3\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ECarbon Dioxide Range:\u003C\/strong\u003E 0 to 2,000PPM\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EAccuracy:\u003C\/strong\u003E 50PPM\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EConnection:\u003C\/strong\u003E Harwired\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EHousing:\u003C\/strong\u003E White plastic\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EDimensions:\u003C\/strong\u003E 4.6 x 3.3 x 1.2\" | 116 x 84 x 30mm\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ESensor Series:\u003C\/strong\u003E 4-20mA Series\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ENotes:\u003C\/strong\u003E Requires a 24VDC power supply FGD-0070\u003C\/p\u003E\n\u003Ch3\u003EDownloads\u003C\/h3\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\u003Ca href=\"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0987\/4738\/4122\/files\/FGD-0068_CS.pdf\"\u003E4-20mA Type Carbon Dioxide (CO2) Sensor Sales Brochure\u003C\/a\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Ca href=\"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0987\/4738\/4122\/files\/LIT-0153_CO2instructions.pdf\"\u003E4-20mA Type Carbon Dioxide (CO2) Sensor Instructions\u003C\/a\u003E\u003C\/p\u003E","vendor":"Sensaphone","product_type":"physical","created_at":"2026-02-18T01:47:24-05:00","handle":"4-20ma-type-carbon-dioxide-co2-sensor","updated_at":"2026-02-18T01:47:25-05:00","published_at":"2026-02-18T01:47:19-05:00","template_suffix":null,"published_scope":"global","tags":"BRAND__Sensaphone, CAT__Air Quality Sensors__VAL, MAINSKU__FGD-0068, OLD__149__ID, TYPE__physical","status":"active","admin_graphql_api_id":"gid:\/\/shopify\/Product\/10201315180858","variants":[{"id":53038661239098,"product_id":10201315180858,"title":"Default Title","price":"309.00","position":1,"inventory_policy":"continue","compare_at_price":null,"option1":"Default Title","option2":null,"option3":null,"created_at":"2026-02-18T01:47:25-05:00","updated_at":"2026-02-18T01:47:25-05:00","taxable":true,"barcode":"","fulfillment_service":"manual","grams":0,"inventory_management":"shopify","requires_shipping":true,"sku":"FGD-0068","weight":0,"weight_unit":"lb","inventory_item_id":55065765445946,"inventory_quantity":0,"old_inventory_quantity":0,"admin_graphql_api_id":"gid:\/\/shopify\/ProductVariant\/53038661239098","image_id":null}],"options":[{"id":12742206882106,"product_id":10201315180858,"name":"Title","position":1,"values":["Default Title"]}],"images