[2026-02-18 07:47:51] [INFO] Product variant images has been updated - Shopidy ID - 10201315311930 - BC id=151 => {"product":{"id":10201315311930,"title":"4-20mA Outdoor Carbon Dioxide (CO2) Transmitter","body_html":"\u003Cul\u003E\n\u003Cli style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003EMeasures carbon dioxide from 0 to 20,000 PPM\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003EAccurate to \u00b130 PPM\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003ESet high and low limits by programming the Sensaphone\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003ESensaphone will go into alarm when carbon dioxide level exceeds limit\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003EHighly accurate and reliable Non-dispersive Infrared (NDIR) with state-of-the-art digital linearization and temperature compensated circuitry\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003EWeatherproof enclosure allows monitoring in harsh conditions\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003C\/ul\u003E\u003Cp style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003EThe Sensaphone Carbon Dioxide Sensor will measure and provide real time carbon dioxide values to any Sensaphone that accepts a 4-20mA signal. When the carbon dioxide level falls outside of the Sensaphone\u2019s programmed high or low limit, the user will receive an alarm which displays or reads the current humidity value. The sensor can be programed to detect carbon dioxide levels from 0 to 20,000 PPM. It is ideal for applications where higher levels of CO2 would be expected (&gt;2,000 ppm) such as breweries, wineries, plant greenhouses or where the building will generally be constantly occupied such as a hospital. The weatherproof enclosure allows the sensor to be placed in areas that would typically shorten the life of other sensors. A 24V DC power supply is required to power the sensor.\u003C\/p\u003E\n\u003Ch3\u003EDownloads\u003C\/h3\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\u003Ca href=\"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0987\/4738\/4122\/files\/FGD-0068-OD_CS.pdf\"\u003E4-20mA Outdoor Carbon Dioxide (CO2) Transmitter Sales Brochure\u003C\/a\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Ca href=\"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0987\/4738\/4122\/files\/LIT-0192_CO2instructions.pdf\"\u003E4-20mA Outdoor Carbon Dioxide (CO2) Transmitter Instructions\u003C\/a\u003E\u003C\/p\u003E","vendor":"Sensaphone","product_type":"physical","created_at":"2026-02-18T01:47:50-05:00","handle":"4-20ma-outdoor-carbon-dioxide-co2-transmitter","updated_at":"2026-02-18T01:47:50-05:00","published_at":"2026-02-18T01:47:46-05:00","template_suffix":null,"published_scope":"global","tags":"BRAND__Sensaphone, MAINSKU__FGD-0068-OD, OLD__151__ID, TYPE__physical","status":"active","admin_graphql_api_id":"gid:\/\/shopify\/Product\/10201315311930","variants":[{"id":53038662058298,"product_id":10201315311930,"title":"Default Title","price":"599.00","position":1,"inventory_policy":"continue","compare_at_price":null,"option1":"Default Title","option2":null,"option3":null,"created_at":"2026-02-18T01:47:50-05:00","updated_at":"2026-02-18T01:47:51-05:00","taxable":true,"barcode":"","fulfillment_service":"manual","grams":0,"inventory_management":"shopify","requires_shipping":true,"sku":"FGD-0068-OD","weight":0,"weight_unit":"lb","inventory_item_id":55065766265146,"inventory_quantity":0,"old_inventory_quantity":0,"admin_graphql_api_id":"gid:\/\/shopify\/ProductVariant\/53038662058298","image_id":null}],"options":[{"id":12742207013178,"product_id":10201315311930,"name":"Title","position":1,"values":["Default Title"]}],"images":[{"id":55073501937978,"alt":"151_main_image_0","position":1,"product_id":10201315311930,"created_at":"2026-02-18T01:47:50-05:00","updated_at":"2026-02-18T01:47:50-05:00","admin_graphql_api_id":"gid:\/\/shopify\/MediaImage\/45112689819962","width":1648,"height":2269,"src":"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0987\/4738\/4122\/files\/PH_FGD-0068-OD_Left_HighRes__30953.jpg?v=1771397270","variant_ids":[]},{"id":55073501970746,"alt":"151_main_image_1"