[2026-02-18 07:48:16] [INFO] Product variant images has been updated - Shopidy ID - 10201315541306 - BC id=154 => {"product":{"id":10201315541306,"title":"24VDC Power Supply Accessory for 4-20mA Sensors w\/ Battery Backup","body_html":"\u003Ch3\u003EPower supply with battery backup\u003C\/h3\u003E\n\u003Cul\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003ETwo individual 24VDC outputs for powering 4-20 loops\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003EMax combined output current: 50mA\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E2-prong North-American style input connector (90-264VAC input)\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003EAutomatically switches to battery power when main power is lost\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003ERechargeable and replaceable AA NiMH backup batteries (included)\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003ELasts up to 24 hours on fully charged batteries\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003ESurge protected input\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003ESelf-resetting fused output protects loop powered devices\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003C\/ul\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E4-20mA type transducers require an external power supply to operate when used with most Sensaphone devices. The 24VDC Power Supply with Battery Backup provides two parallel 24V outputs that can be used to power up to two 4-20mA transducers or any 24VDC device that requires battery backup. The unit includes (4) AA NiMh rechargeable batteries that will keep the transducers running for up to 24 hours in the event of a power failure. These devices are available with a domestic or international power supply.\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E\u003C!-- pagebreak --\u003E\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/p\u003E\n\u003Ch3\u003EDownloads\u003C\/h3\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\u003Ca href=\"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0987\/4738\/4122\/files\/FGD-0070_CS.pdf\"\u003E24VDC Power Supply Accessory for 4-20mA Sensors w\/ Battery Backup Sales Brochure\u003C\/a\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Ca href=\"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0987\/4738\/4122\/files\/FG