[2026-02-18 07:48:47] [INFO] Product variant images has been updated - Shopidy ID - 10201315770682 - BC id=159 => {"product":{"id":10201315770682,"title":"4-20mA Type Soil Moisture Sensor","body_html":"\u003Ch3\u003EResearch grade accuracy\u003C\/h3\u003E\n\u003Cul\u003E\n\u003Cli style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003EMeasures soil moisture from 0 to 100% VWC\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003EUses a 70 MHz frequency, which minimizes salinity and textural effects, making the MAS-1 accurate in almost any soil or soil-less media\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003EFactory calibrations are included for mineral soils, potting soils, and rockwool\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003ESet high and low limits by programming the Sensaphone\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003ESensaphone will go into alarm when soil moisture level exceeds limit\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003EDelivers research-grade accuracy\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003C\/ul\u003E\u003Cp style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003EThe Sensaphone Soil Moisture Sensor will measure and provide real time moisture values to any Sensaphone that accepts a 4-20mA signal. When the soil moisture level falls outside of the Sensaphone\u2019s programmed high or low limit, the user will receive an alarm which displays or reads the current moisture value. The sensor determines volumetric water content (VWC) by measuring the dielectric constant of the media using capacitance\/frequency domain technology. It minimizes salinity and textural effects, making it accurate in almost any soil or soil-less media. Factory calibrations are included for mineral soils, potting soils, and rockwool. A 24V DC power supply is required to power the sensor\u003Cspan\u003E\u00a0\u003C\/span\u003E(Part # FGD-0070)\u003Cspan\u003E.\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E\u003C!-- pagebreak --\u003E\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/p\u003E\n\u003Ch3\u003E\u003Cspan\u003ETechnical Specifications\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/h3\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EOperating Temperature Range:\u003C\/strong\u003E -40\u00b0 to 140\u00b0F | -40\u00b0 to 60\u00b0C\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EScale:\u003C\/strong\u003E 0 - 100% VWC (Volumetric Water Content)\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EAccuracy:\u003C\/strong\u003E 6% VWC with generic calibration for supported growing media up to 65% VWC, above which accuracy lessens. Increased accuracy can be achieved with a medium-specific calibration.\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EConnection:\u003C\/strong\u003E Hardwired\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ESettling Time:\u003C\/strong\u003E 4 seconds\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EDimensions:\u003C\/strong\u003E 3.5 x .27 x .7\" | 89mm x 18 mm x 7mm\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ESensor Series:\u003C\/strong\u003E 4-20mA\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ENotes:\u003C\/strong\u003E Requires a 24VDC power supply (FGD-0070)\u003C\/span\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/p\u003E\n\u003Ch3\u003E\u003Cspan\u003EDownloads\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/h3\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E\u003Ca href=\"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0987\/4738\/4122\/files\/FGD-0090_CS.pdf\"\u003E4-20mA Type Soil Moisture Sensor Sales Brochure\u003C\/a\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Ca href=\"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0987\/4738\/4122\/files\/LIT-0161_SoilMoisture_Instructions.pdf\"\u003E4-20mA Type Soil Moisture Sensor Instructions\u003C\/a\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/p\u003E","vendor":"Sensaphone","product_type":"physical","created_at":"2026-02-18T01:48:45-05:00","handle":"4-20ma-type-soil-moisture-sensor","updated_at":"2026-02-18T01:48:46-05:00","published_at":"2026-02-18T01:48:43-05:00","template_suffix":null,"published_scope":"global","tags":"BRAND__Sensaphone, CAT__Accessories__VAL, MAINSKU__FGD-0090, OLD__159__ID, TYPE__physical","status":"active","admin_graphql_api_id":"gid:\/\/sh