[2026-02-18 07:49:20] [INFO] Product variant images has been updated - Shopidy ID - 10201316065594 - BC id=165 => {"product":{"id":10201316065594,"title":"10K Type Outdoor Air Temperature Sensor","body_html":"\u003Ch3\u003EMinimize radiant energy effects\u003C\/h3\u003E\n\u003Cul\u003E\n\u003Cli style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003EMeasures temperature from -30\u00b0 to 140\u00b0F | -34\u00b0 to 60\u00b0C\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003EAccurate to \u00b1 .36\u00b0F |\u003Cspan\u003E\u00a0 \u003C\/span\u003E\u00b1 .2\u00b0C\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003EIncludes mounting hardware\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003EPVC shield minimizes radiant energy effects on temperature readings\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003ESuitable for use in outdoor environments\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003C\/ul\u003E\u003Cp style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003EThe Outdoor Weatherproof Temperature Sensor can be used with most Sensaphone models to measure the ambient air temperature without the effects of being in direct sunlight. When the temperature falls outside of the Sensaphone\u2019s programmed high or low limit, the user will receive an alarm which displays or reads the current temperature. The temperature sensor is mounted inside a ventilated, treated weather\u2013resistant PVC shield to minimize radiant energy effects and mounted on a weatherproof outlet box for easy installation. The sensor connects to the Sensaphone with the included 8\u2019 of wire and can be extended using optional accessory wire.\u003C\/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E\u003C!-- pagebreak --\u003E\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/p\u003E\n\u003Ch3\u003E\u003Cspan\u003ETechnical Specifications\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/h3\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ESensor Temperature Range:\u003C\/strong\u003E -30\u00b0 to 140\u00b0F | -34\u00b0 to 60\u00b0C\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EAccuracy:\u003C\/strong\u003E .36\u00b0F | .2\u00b0C\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EConnection:\u003C\/strong\u003E Hardwired\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EHousing:\u003C\/strong\u003E PVC Shield, Weatherproof Metal Outlet Box\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EDimensions:\u003C\/strong\u003E 9 x 3 x 2\" | 228 x 76 x 51mm\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ESensor Series:\u003C\/strong\u003E 10k Series\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/p\u003E\n\u003Ch3\u003E\u003Cspan\u003EDownloads\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/h3\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\u003Ca href=\"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0987\/4738\/4122\/files\/FGD-0104_CS.pdf\"\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E10K Type Outdoor Air Temperature Sensor Sales Brochure\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/a\u003E\u003C\/p\u003E","vendor":"Sensaphone","product_type":"physical","created_at":"2026-02-18T01:49:19-05:00","handle":"10k-type-outdoor-air-temperature-sensor","updated_at":"2026-02-18T01:49:19-05:00","published_at":"2026-02-18T01:49:17-05:00","template_suffix":null,"published_scope":"global","tags":"BRAND__Sensaphone, CAT__Temperature Sensors__VAL, MAINSKU__FGD-0104, OLD__165__ID, TYPE__physical","status":"active","admin_graphql_api_id":"gid:\/\/shopify\/Product\/10201316065594","variants":[{"id":53038665302330,"product_id":10201316065594,"title":"Default Title","price":"70.00","position":1,"inventory_policy":"continue","compare_at_price":null,"option1":"Default Title","option2":null,"option3":null,"created_at":"2026-02-18T01:49:19-05:00","updated_at":"2026-02-18T01:49:20-05:00","taxable":true,"barcode":"","fulfillment_service":"manual","grams":0,"inventory_management":"shopify","requires_shipping":true,"sku":"FGD-0104","weight":0,"weight_unit":"lb","inventory_item_id":55065769509178,"inventory_quantity":0,"old_inventory_quantity":0,"admin_graphql_api_id":"gid:\/\/shopify\/ProductVariant\/53038665302330","image_id":null}],"options":[{"id":12742207766842,"product_id":10201316065594,"name":"Title","position":1,"values":["Default Title"]}],"images":[{"id":55073508950330,"alt":"165_main_