[2026-02-18 07:49:29] [INFO] Product variant images has been updated - Shopidy ID - 10201316098362 - BC id=166 => {"product":{"id":10201316098362,"title":"10K Type Immersion Temperature Sensor","body_html":"\u003Ch3\u003EFluid temperature monitoring\u003C\/h3\u003E\n\u003Cul\u003E\n\u003Cli style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003EMeasures temperature from 40\u00b0 to 221\u00b0F | -34\u00b0 to 60\u00b0C\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003EAccurate to \u00b1 .36\u00b0F |\u003Cspan\u003E\u00a0 \u003C\/span\u003E\u00b1 .2\u00b0C\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003EMeasures temperature of fluid inside a pipe\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003C\/ul\u003E\u003Cp style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003EThe Immersion Temperature Sensor can be used with most Sensaphone models to measure the temperature of fluids inside a pipe. When the temperature falls outside of the Sensaphone\u2019s programmed high or low limit, the user will receive an alarm which displays or reads the current temperature. It\u2019s constructed of brass WEL-B thermowell which screws into a customer-supplied 0.5\u201d NPT saddle or Thredolet\u00ae fitting in a pipe. It fits into a thermowell via a brass 0.125\u201d NPT fitting. The sensor connects to the Sensaphone with the attached 8\u2019 of wire and can be extended using optional accessory wire.\u003C\/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E\u003C!-- pagebreak --\u003E\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/p\u003E\n\u003Ch3\u003E\u003Cspan\u003ETechnical Specifications\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/h3\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ESensor Temperature Range\u003C\/strong\u003E: -40\u00b0 to 221\u00b0F | -40\u00b0 to 105\u00b0C\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EAccuracy:\u003C\/strong\u003E .36\u00b0F | .2\u00b0C\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EConnection:\u003C\/strong\u003E Hardwired\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EHousing:\u003C\/strong\u003E Brass\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EDimensions:\u003C\/strong\u003E Thermowell: 5.2\" | 130mm\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ESensor Series:\u003C\/strong\u003E 10k Series\u003Cbr\u003E\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/p\u003E\n\u003Ch3\u003E\u003Cspan\u003EDownloads\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/h3\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E\u003Ca href=\"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0987\/4738\/4122\/files\/FGD-0105_CS.pdf\"\u003E10K Type Immersion Temperature Sensor Sales Brochure\u003C\/a\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Ca href=\"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0987\/4738\/4122\/files\/FGD-0105%20Instructions_WEB.pdf\"\u003E10K Type Immersion Temperature Sensor Instructions\u003C\/a\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003C\/span\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/p\u003E","vendor":"Sensaphone","product_type":"physical","created_at":"2026-02-18T01:49:27-05:00","handle":"10k-type-immersion-temperature-sensor","updated_at":"2026-02-18T01:49:28-05:00","published_at":"2026-02-18T01:49:25-05:00","template_suffix":null,"published_scope":"global","tags":"BRAND__Sensaphone, CAT__Temperature Sensors__VAL, MAINSKU__FGD-0105, OLD__166__ID, TYPE__physical","status":"active","admin_graphql_api_id":"gid:\/\/shopify\/Product\/10201316098362","variants":[{"id":53038665662778,"product_id":10201316098362,"title":"Default Title","price":"65.00","position":1,"inventory_policy":"continue","compare_at_price":null,"option1":"Default Title","option2":null,"option3":null,"created_at":"2026-02-18T01:49:28-05:00","updated_at":"2026-02-18T01:49:28-05:00","taxable":true,"barcode":"","fulfillment_service":"manual","grams":0,"inventory_management":"shopify","requires_shipping":true,"sku":"FGD-0105","weight":0,"weight_unit":"lb","inventory_item_id":55065769869626,"inventory_quantity":0,"old_inventory_quantity":0,"admin_graphql_api_id":"gid:\/\/shopify\/ProductVariant\/53038665662778","image_id":null}],"options":[{"id":12742207799610,"product_id":10201316098362,"name":"Title","position":1,"values":["Default Title"]}],"images":[{"id":55073509572922,"alt":"166_main_image_0","position":1,"product_id"