[2026-02-18 07:49:44] [INFO] Product variant images has been updated - Shopidy ID - 10201316229434 - BC id=169 => {"product":{"id":10201316229434,"title":"2.8K Type Ultra Low Temperature Sensor in Glass Bead Vial","body_html":"\u003Ch3\u003EBuffer momentary temperature fluctuations\u003C\/h3\u003E\n\u003Cul\u003E\n\u003Cli style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003EMeasures temperature from -121\u00b0 to 176\u00b0F | -85\u00b0 to 80\u00b0C\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003EAccurate to \u00b1 1\u00b0F |\u003Cspan\u003E\u00a0 \u003C\/span\u003E\u00b1 .56\u00b0C\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003EGlass bead filled vial provides representation of temperature of freezers contents\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003EHelps to buffer any momentary fluctuations that may cause a preliminary alarm\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003EIncludes 12\u2019 of wire\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003ESuitable for use in wet or dirty environments\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003C\/ul\u003E\u003Cp style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003EThe Ultra Low Temperature Sensor in Glass Bead Vial can be used with all Sensaphone models to measure the temperature of objects in a freezer. By placing the sensor in a bottle filled with glass beads users will receive a reading that represents the temperature of the freezer\u2019s contents rather than the ambient air temperature. The Sensaphone will trigger an alarm when the temperature falls outside of the programmed high or low temperature limit. The sensor\u2019s coated wire prevents cracking and allows it to be placed inside of freezers that go as low as -85\u00b0C. The glass bead filled vial will also buffer any momentary fluctuations that may cause a preliminary alarm dial out, such as defrost cycles, opening of doors, and fans circulating air. The glass beads will slow the response time of the sensor allowing normal daily operations to occur without having an alarm. The included 12 feet of coated wire can be extended with optional accessory wire.\u003C\/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003EAn optional NIST traceable certificate is available.\u003C\/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E\u003C!-- pagebreak --\u003E\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/p\u003E\n\u003Ch3\u003E\u003Cspan\u003ETechnical Specifications\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/h3\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ESensor Temperature Range:\u003C\/strong\u003E -121\u00b0 to 176\u00b0F | -85\u00b0 to 80\u00b0C\u00a0\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EAccuracy:\u003C\/strong\u003E 1\u00b0F | .56\u00b0C\u00a0\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EConnection:\u003C\/strong\u003E Hardwired\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EHousing:\u003C\/strong\u003E 30mL HDPE Plastic\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EDimensions:\u003C\/strong\u003E 1.34 x 2.48\" | 34mm x 63mm\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ESensor Series:\u003C\/strong\u003E 2.8K\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ENotes:\u003C\/strong\u003E Available with NIST Certification\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/p\u003E\n\u003Ch3\u003EDownloads\u003C\/h3\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\u003Ca href=\"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0987\/4738\/4122\/files\/FGD-0107_TEF_CS.pdf\"\u003E2.8K Type Ultra Low Temperature Sensor in Glass Bead Vial Sales Brochure\u003C\/a\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Ca href=\"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0987\/4738\/4122\/files\/LIT-0218_BufferedTempInstructions.pdf\"\u003E2.8K Type Ultra Low Temperature Sensor in Glass Bead Vial Instructions\u003C\/a\u003E\u003C\/p\u003E","vendor":"Sensaphone","product_type":"physical","created_at":"2026-02-18T01:49:43-05:00","handle":"28k-type-ultra-low-temperature-sensor-in-glass-bead-vial","updated_at":"2026-02-18T01:49:43-05:00","published_at":"2026-02-18T01:49:41-05:00","template_suffix":null,"published_scope":"global","tags":"BRAND__Sensaphone, CAT__Temperature Sensors__VAL, OLD__169__ID, TYPE__physical","status":"active","admin_graphql_api_id":"gid:\/\/sho