[2026-02-18 07:49:55] [INFO] Product variant images has been updated - Shopidy ID - 10201316360506 - BC id=171 => {"product":{"id":10201316360506,"title":"Modbus Type Temperature and Humidity Combination Sensor","body_html":"\u003Ch3\u003EMonitor Temperature and Humidity from one point\u003C\/h3\u003E\n\u003Cul\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003ESingle point solution for monitoring indoor air temperature and humidity\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003EMeasures temperature from 32\u00b0 to 122\u00b0F | 0\u00b0 to 50\u00b0C\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003ETemperature accurate: \u00b1 .4\u00b0F |\u00a0 \u00b1 .2\u00b0C\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003EMeasures humidity from 0-100% RH, non condensing\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003C\/ul\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan\u003EThis combination temperature and humidity sensor is used exclusively with Sensaphone \u003C\/span\u003ESentinel Pro and Stratus EMS\u003Cspan\u003E models to measure the temperature and humidity in a clean, dry environment. The Sensaphone will trigger an alarm when the temperature or humidity falls outside of the programmed high or low limit. It features include a back-lit LCD and user menu for easy installation. The slim enclosure allows the sensor to be mounted in in a single gang electrical box or directly to the wall. A 24V DC power supply is required to power the sensor.\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E\u003C!-- pagebreak --\u003E\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/p\u003E\n\u003Ch3\u003E\u003Cspan\u003ETechnical Specifications\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/h3\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ESensor Temperature Range\u003C\/strong\u003E: 32\u00b0 to 122\u00b0F | -0\u00b0 to 50\u00b0C\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ETemperature Accuracy:\u003C\/strong\u003E .4\u00b0F | .2\u00b0C\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EHumidity Range:\u003C\/strong\u003E 0-100% RH, non-condensing\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EHumidity Accuracy:\u003C\/strong\u003E 2% RH\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EPower Supply:\u003C\/strong\u003E 20-28 VAC\/DC (non-isolated half-wave rectified)\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EDimensions:\u003C\/strong\u003E 3.3 x 4.7 x 1.15\" | 84 x 119 x 29mm\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ESensor Series:\u003C\/strong\u003E Modbus Series - 2 wire RS-485\u003Cbr\u003E\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/p\u003E\n\u003Ch3\u003E\u003Cspan\u003EDownloads\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/h3\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E\u003Ca href=\"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0987\/4738\/4122\/files\/FGD-0110_CS.pdf\"\u003EModbus Type Temperature and Humidity Combination Sensor Sales Brochure\u003C\/a\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Ca href=\"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0987\/4738\/4122\/files\/LIT-0205_Temp-Hum_Instructions.pdf\"\u003EModbus Type Temperature and Humidity Combination Sensor Instructions\u003C\/a\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/p\u003E","vendor":"Sensaphone","product_type":"physical","created_at":"2026-02-18T01:49:53-05:00","handle":"modbus-type-temperature-and-humidity-combination-sensor","updated_at":"2026-02-18T01:49:53-05:00","published_at":"2026-02-18T01:49:51-05:00","template_suffix":null,"published_scope":"global","tags":"BRAND__Sensaphone, CAT__Humidity Sensors__VAL, CAT__Temperature Sensors__VAL, MAINSKU__FGD-0110, OLD__171__ID, TYPE__physical","status":"active","admin_graphql_api_id":"gid:\/\/shopify\/Product\/10201316360506","variants":[{"id":53038666875194,"product_id":10201316360506,"title":"Default Title","price":"229.00","position":1,"inventory_policy":"continue","compare_at_price":null,"option1":"Default Title","option2":null,"option3":null,"created_at":"2026-02-18T01:49:53-05:00","updated_at":"2026-02-18T01:49:54-05:00","taxable":true,"barcode":"","fulfillment_service":"manual","grams":0,"inventory_management":"shopify","requires_shipping":true,"sku":"FGD-0110","weight":0,"weight_unit":"lb","inventory_item_id":55065771082042,"inventory_quantity":0,"old_inventory_quantity":0,"admin_graphql_api_id":"gid:\/\/shopify\/ProductVariant\/