[2026-02-18 07:50:25] [INFO] Product variant images has been updated - Shopidy ID - 10201316622650 - BC id=175 => {"product":{"id":10201316622650,"title":"2.8k Type Temperature Sensor in Glycol Vial","body_html":"\u003Ch3\u003EBuffer momentary temperature fluctuations\u003C\/h3\u003E\n\u003Cul\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003EMeasures temperature from -20\u00b0 to 176\u00b0F | -28\u00b0 to 80\u00b0C\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003EAccurate to \u00b1 1\u00b0F |\u00a0 \u00b1 .56\u00b0C\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003EGlycol filled vial will buffer any momentary fluctuations that may cause a preliminary alarm\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003EIncludes 12\u2019 of wire\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003C\/ul\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan\u003EThe Temperature Sensor in Glycol Vial can be used with most Sensaphone models to measure the temperature of objects in a refrigerator or freezer. By placing the sensor in a bottle filled with glycol, users will receive a reading that represents the temperature of the refrigerator\u2019s contents rather than the ambient air temperature. The Sensaphone will trigger an alarm when the temperature falls outside of the programmed high or low temperature limit. The glycol filled vial will also buffer any momentary fluctuations that may cause a preliminary alarm dial out, such as defrost cycles, the opening of doors, and fans circulating air. The glycol will slow the response time of the sensor, allowing normal daily operations to occur without having an alarm. The included 12 feet of wire can be extended with optional accessory wire.\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E\u003C!-- pagebreak --\u003E\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/p\u003E\n\u003Ch4\u003E\u003Cspan\u003ETechnical Specifications:\u003Cbr\u003E\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/h4\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ESensor Temperature Range:\u003C\/strong\u003E -20\u00b0 to 176\u00b0F | -28\u00b0 to 80\u00b0C\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EAccuracy:\u003C\/strong\u003E 1\u00b0F | .56\u00b0C\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EConnection:\u003C\/strong\u003E Hardwired\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EHousing:\u003C\/strong\u003E HDPE Plastic\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EDimensions:\u003C\/strong\u003E 2.8 x 1.6\" | 72mm x 40mm \u00a0\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ESensor Series:\u003C\/strong\u003E 2.8k\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ENotes:\u003C\/strong\u003E Available with NIST Certification\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/p\u003E\n\u003Ch3\u003E\u003Cspan\u003EDownloads\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/h3\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E\u003Ca href=\"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0987\/4738\/4122\/files\/FGD-0127-TEF_CS.pdf\"\u003E2.8k Type Temperature Sensor in Glycol Vial Sales Brochure\u003C\/a\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Ca href=\"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0987\/4738\/4122\/files\/LIT-0218_BufferedTempInstructions.pdf\"\u003E2.8k Type Temperature Sensor in Glycol Vial Instructions\u003C\/a\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/p\u003E","vendor":"Sensaphone","product_type":"physical","created_at":"2026-02-18T01:50:23-05:00","handle":"28k-type-temperature-sensor-in-glycol-vial","updated_at":"2026-02-18T01:50:24-05:00","published_at":"2026-02-18T01:50:22-05:00","template_suffix":null,"published_scope":"global","tags":"BRAND__Sensaphone, CAT__Temperature Sensors__VAL, OLD__175__ID, TYPE__physical","status":"active","admin_graphql_api_id":"gid:\/\/shopify\/Product\/10201316622650","variants":[{"id":53038668251450,"product_id":10201316622650,"title":"None","price":"55.00","position":1,"inventory_policy":"continue","compare_at_price":null,"option1":"None","option2":null,"option3":null,"created_at":"2026-02-18T01:50:24-05:00","updated_at":"2026-02-18T01:50:24-05:00","taxable":true,"barcode":"","fulfillment_service":"manual","grams":0,"inventory_management":"shopify","requires_shipping":true,"sku":"FGD-0127","weight":0,"weight_unit":"lb","inventory_item_id":55065772458298,"inventory_quantity":0,"old_inventory_quantity":0,"admin_g