[2026-02-18 07:50:36] [INFO] Product variant images has been updated - Shopidy ID - 10201316753722 - BC id=179 => {"product":{"id":10201316753722,"title":"J Type Thermocouple \/ 4-20mA Converter","body_html":"\u003Ch3\u003EOut of range temperature monitoring\u003C\/h3\u003E\n\u003Cul\u003E\n\u003Cli style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003EMeasures temperature from -148\u00b0 to 572\u00b0F | -100\u00b0 to 300\u00b0C\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003EAccurate to 0.08%\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003EThe sensor will put out an analog current scaled from 4 to 20mA corresponding to the measurement range of the sensor\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003EScrew Terminals and Plug-in Terminal Blocks Simplify Wiring and Maintenance\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003EC-UL-US Listed (Class I, Division 2, Groups A, B, C, D)\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003C\/ul\u003E\u003Cp\u003EThe J Type Thermocouple \/ 4-20mA Converter can be used with any Sensaphone model that accepts a 4-20mA signal to measure temperatures that are beyond the Sensaphone\u2019s temperature sensing range. The converter allows monitoring of temperatures from -148\u00b0 to 572\u00b0F. The Sensaphone will trigger an alarm when the temperature falls outside of the programmed high or low temperature limit. Optional accessory wire is required for installation.\u003C\/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E\u003C!-- pagebreak --\u003E\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/p\u003E\n\u003Ch3\u003E\u003Cspan\u003ETechnical Specifications\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/h3\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ESensor Temperature Range:\u003C\/strong\u003E -148\u00b0 to 572\u00b0F | -100\u00b0 to 300\u00b0C\u00a0\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EAccuracy:\u003C\/strong\u003E 0.08%\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EThermocouple Type:\u003C\/strong\u003E J (not included)\u00a0\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EOutput Range:\u003C\/strong\u003E 4 to 20mA\u