[2026-02-18 07:50:49] [INFO] Product variant images has been updated - Shopidy ID - 10201316950330 - BC id=181 => {"product":{"id":10201316950330,"title":"Contact Type Float Level Switch","body_html":"\u003Ch3\u003EMonitor fluid levels\u003C\/h3\u003E\n\u003Cul\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003ESide mounted float switch\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003ECan be rotated for Normally Open or Normally Closed operation\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003EContact rating: 50W\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003EMax switch voltage: 100VDC\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003C\/ul\u003E\u003Cp style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003EThe Float Level Switch can be used with all Sensaphone models to monitor for rise or fall of fluids in a well or tank. When the sensor detects the switch opening or closing due to the tank filling or draining, it will trigger the Sensaphone to go into alarm. It is cost effective for level control applications in small tanks where it is more convenient to install a level switch through the sidewall of the tank. This style float switch can be rotated for Normally Open or Normally Closed operation. Combine two switches at different levels for high and low level or pump control or alarming. The sensor requires no additional power for operation and is connected to the Sensaphone via accessory wire (not included).\u003C\/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E\u003C!-- pagebreak --\u003E\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/p\u003E\n\u003Ch3\u003E\u003Cspan\u003ETechnical Specifications\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/h3\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EOperating Range:\u003C\/strong\u003E -10\u00b0 to 80\u00b0F | -23\u00b0 to 26\u00b0C\u00a0\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EContact Rating:\u003C\/strong\u003E 50W\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EMax Switch Voltage:\u003C\/strong\u003E 100VDC\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EConnection:\u003C\/strong\u003E Hardwired\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EHousing:\u003C\/strong\u003E Plastic\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EDimensions:\u003C\/strong\u003E 3.5 x 1.5\" | 89 x 38mm\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ESensor Series:\u003C\/strong\u003E Contact Series\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/p\u003E\n\u003Ch3\u003E\u003Cspan\u003EDownloads\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/h3\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E\u003Ca href=\"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0987\/4738\/4122\/files\/FGD-0222_CS.pdf\"\u003EContact Type Float Level Switch Sales Brochure\u003C\/a\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Ca href=\"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0987\/4738\/4122\/files\/LIT-0149_FGD-0222Instructions.pdf\"\u003EContact Type Float Level Switch Instructions\u003C\/a\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/p\u003E","vendor":"Sensaphone","product_type":"physical","created_at":"2026-02-18T01:50:47-05:00","handle":"contact-type-float-level-switch","updated_at":"2026-02-18T01:50:47-05:00","published_at":"2026-02-18T01:50:44-05:00","template_suffix":null,"published_scope":"global","tags":"BRAND__Sensaphone, CAT__Accessories__VAL, MAINSKU__FGD-0222, OLD__181__ID, TYPE__physical","status":"active","admin_graphql_api_id":"gid:\/\/shopify\/Product\/10201316950330","variants":[{"id":53038669594938,"product_id":10201316950330,"title":"Default Title","price":"39.00","position":1,"inventory_policy":"continue","compare_at_price":null,"option1":"Default Title","option2":null,"option3":null,"created_at":"2026-02-18T01:50:47-05:00","updated_at":"2026-02-18T01:50:48-05:00","taxable":true,"barcode":"","fulfillment_service":"manual","grams":0,"inventory_management":"shopify","requires_shipping":true,"sku":"FGD-0222","weight":0,"weight_unit":"lb","inventory_item_id":55065773801786,"inventory_quantity":0,"old_inventory_quantity":0,"admin_graphql_api_id":"gid:\/\/shopify\/ProductVariant\/53038669594938","image_id":null}],"options":[{"id":12742208651578,"product_id":10201316950330,"name":"Title","position":1,"values":["Default Title"]}],"images":[{"id":55073515635002,"alt":"181_main_image_0","position":1,"product_id":10201316950330,"created_at":"2026-02-18T01:50:47-05:00