[2026-02-18 07:51:41] [INFO] Product variant images has been updated - Shopidy ID - 10201317474618 - BC id=190 => {"product":{"id":10201317474618,"title":"4-20mA Type Pressure Sensor","body_html":"\u003Ch3\u003EReceive alarms and datalog pressure values\u003C\/h3\u003E\n\u003Cul\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003EMeasures pressure from 0 to 200 psi, or 0-1,000 psi\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003ERequires a 24VDC power supply FGD-0070\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003ECompatible with refrigerants\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\u003Cspan\u003ESuitable for higher range pressure applications, such as steam boilers and the high side\/discharge lines on HVAC equipment which can exceed 500PSI\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003C\/ul\u003E\u003Cp style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003EThe Sensaphone Pressure Sensor will measure and provide real time pressure values to any Sensaphone that accepts a 4-20mA signal. When the pressure level falls outside of the Sensaphone\u2019s programmed high or low limit, the user will receive an alarm which displays or reads the current pressure value. The sensor can be programed to detect pressure levels from 0 to 200 PSI. An alarm from the pressure sensor can indicate a problem with a pump, a possible clogged influent line, loss of suction, a downstream clog or perhaps a burst pipe. Any of those failures can cause a pump motor to overheat and warp. A 24V DC power supply is required to power the sensor.\u003C\/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E\u003C!-- pagebreak --\u003E\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/p\u003E\n\u003Ch3\u003E\u003Cspan\u003ETechnical Specifications\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/h3\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EProcess connection:\u003C\/strong\u003E 1\/4-18 NPT\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EMeasuring Range:\u003C\/strong\u003E 0 to 200 psi, 0 to 1,000\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EOperating Voltage:\u003C\/strong\u003E 8.5 to 36 DC\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EOutput Function:\u003C\/strong\u003E 4-20mA Analog\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EAccuracy:\u003C\/strong\u003E &lt;0.5\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EOperating Temperature:\u003C\/strong\u003E -40\u00b0F to 194\u00b0F | -40\u00b0C to 90\u00b0C\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EProtection:\u003C\/strong\u003E IP 67 | IP 69K\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EDimensions:\u003C\/strong\u003E 2.63 x .75\" | 66.9 x 18.9mm\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ECable Length:\u003C\/strong\u003E 6.6' | 2m \u00a022AWG\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ENotes:\u003C\/strong\u003E Requires a 24VDC power supply\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/p\u003E\n\u003Ch3\u003EDownloads\u003C\/h3\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\u003Ca href=\"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0987\/4738\/4122\/files\/FGD-0301_CS.pdf\"\u003E4-20mA Type Pressure Sensor Sales Brochure\u003C\/a\u003E\u003C\/p\u003E","vendor":"Sensaphone","product_type":"physical","created_at":"2026-02-18T01:51:39-05:00","handle":"4-20ma-type-pressure-sensor","updated_at":"2026-02-18T01:51:40-05:00","published_at":"2026-02-18T01:51:37-05:00","template_suffix":null,"published_scope":"global","tags":"BRAND__Sensaphone, CAT__Other__VAL, MAINSKU__FGD-0301, OLD__190__ID, TYPE__physical","status":"active","admin_graphql_api_id":"gid:\/\/shopify\/Product\/10201317474618","variants":[{"id":53038672281914,"product_id":10201317474618,"title":"Default Title","price":"149.00","position":1,"inventory_policy":"continue","compare_at_price":null,"option1":"Default Title","option2":null,"option3":null,"created_at":"2026-02-18T01:51:40-05:00","updated_at":"2026-02-18T01:51:40-05:00","taxable":true,"barcode":"","fulfillment_service":"manual","grams":0,"inventory_management":"shopify","requires_shipping":true,"sku":"FGD-0301","weight":0,"weight_unit":"lb","inventory_item_id":55065776488762,"inventory_quantity":0,"old_inventory_quantity":0,"admin_graphql_api_id":"gid:\/\/shopify\/ProductVariant\/53038672281914","image_id":null}],"options":[{"id":12742209241402,"product_id":10201317474618,"name":"Title","position":1,"values":["Default Title"]}],"images":[{"id":55073520484666,"alt":"190_main_image_0","position":1,"product_id":10201317474618,"created_at":"2026-02-18T01:51:39-05:00","updated_at":"2026-02-18T01:51:39-05:00","admin_graphql_api_id":"gid:\/\/shopify\/MediaImage\/45112708006202","width":1000,"height":1000,"src":"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0987\/4738\/4122\/files\/PH_FGD-0301_WaterPressure1__50563.jpg?v=1771397499","variant_ids":[]},{"id":55073520517434,"alt":"-","position":2,"product_id":10201317474618,"created_at":"2026-02-18T01:51:39-05:00","updated_at":"2026-02-18T01:51:40-05:00","admin_graphql_api_id":"gid:\/\/shopify\/MediaImage\/45112708038970","width":386,"height":386,"src":"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0987\/4738\/4122\/files\/PH_FGD-0301_WaterPressure1__50563.1708705917.386.513.jpg?v=1771397499","variant_ids":[]}],"image":{"id":55073520484666,"alt":"190_main_image_0","position":1,"product_id":10201317474618,"created_at":"2026-02-18T01:51:39-05:00","updated_at":"2026-02-18T01:51:39-05:00","admin_graphql_api_id":"gid:\/\/shopify\/MediaImage\/45112708006202","width":1000,"height":1000,"src":"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0987\/4738\/4122\/files\/PH_FGD-0301_WaterPressure1__50563.jpg?v=1771397499","variant_ids":[]}}}
