[2026-02-18 07:51:56] [INFO] Product variant images has been updated - Shopidy ID - 10201317638458 - BC id=191 => {"product":{"id":10201317638458,"title":"4-20mA Type Differential Pressure Sensor","body_html":"\u003Ch3\u003EMeasure static or differential pressure\u003C\/h3\u003E\n\u003Cul\u003E\n\u003Cli style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003EMeasures differential or static pressure\u00a0\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003ESwitch selectable unidirectional or bidirectional mode\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003EIncludes probes and tubing for mounting\u00a0\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003ESet high and low limits by programming the Sensaphone\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003ESensaphone will go into alarm when pressure level exceeds limit\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003C\/ul\u003E\u003Cp style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003EThe Sensaphone Differential Air Pressure Sensor will measure and provide real time differential or static pressure values to any Sensaphone that accepts a 4-20mA signal. When the pressure level falls outside of the Sensaphone\u2019s programmed high or low limit, the user will receive an alarm which displays or reads the current differential or static pressure value. The high accuracy digital sensor maintains calibration, reduces callbacks and provides an excellent tolerance to overpressure and vibration. Monitoring for positive and negative pressures provides application versatility and the LCD is ideal for set-up, troubleshooting, and measuring. A 24V DC power supply is required to power the sensor. Choose between a wall or duct mount sensor.\u003C\/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E\u003C!-- pagebreak --\u003E\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/p\u003E\n\u003Ch4\u003E\u003Cspan\u003ETechnical Specifications\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/h4\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EMedia Compatibility:\u003C\/strong\u003E Dry air or inert gas\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EInput Power:\u003C\/strong\u003E 2-wire, loop-powered 4-20mA\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EMode:\u003C\/strong\u003E Unidirectional or bidirectional, switch selectable\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EPressure Ranges:\u003C\/strong\u003E Uni Directional: 0.1\/0.25\/0.5\/1.0\/2.5\/5\/10 W.C. 25 Pa\/50 Pa\/100 Pa\/250 Pa\/0.5 kPa\/1 kPa\/2.5 kPa F.S. switch selectable\u003Cbr\u003EBi Directional: 0.1\/0.25\/0.5\/1.0\/2.5\/5\/10 W.C. 25 Pa\/50 Pa\/100 Pa\/250 Pa\/0.5 kPa\/1 kPa\/2.5 kPa F.S. switch selectable\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EDimensions:\u003C\/strong\u003E 3.3 x 4.5 x 2.2\" | 84mm x 114mm x 55mm\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ESensor Series:\u003C\/strong\u003E 4-20mA\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ENotes:\u003C\/strong\u003E Requires a 24VDC power supply FGD-0070\u003C\/p\u003E\n\u003Ch3\u003EDownloads\u003C\/h3\u003E\n\u003Cdiv\u003E\u003Ca href=\"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0987\/4738\/4122\/files\/FGD-0302-ROOM_CS.pdf\"\u003ESensaphone Room Differential Pressure Sensor Cutsheet\u003C\/a\u003E\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv\u003E\n\u003Cdiv\u003E\n\u003Cdiv\u003E\u003Ca href=\"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0987\/4738\/4122\/files\/FGD-0302-DUCT_CS.pdf\"\u003ESensaphone Duct Differential Pressure Sensor Cutsheet\u003C\/a\u003E\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv\u003E\u003Ca href=\"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0987\/4738\/4122\/files\/LIT-0186_Pressure_Instructions_B.pdf\"\u003ESensaphone Differential Pressure Sensor Instructions\u003C\/a\u003E\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv\u003E\u00a0\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv\u003E\u00a0\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003C\/div\u003E","vendor":"Sensaphone","product_type":"physical","created_at":"2026-02-18T01:51:54-05:00","handle":"4-20ma-type-differential-pressure-sensor","updated_at":"2026-02-18T01:51:54-05:00","published_at":"2026-02-18T01:51:48-05:00","template_suffix":null,"published_scope":"global","tags":"BRAND__Sensaphone, CAT__Other__VAL, OLD__191__ID, TYPE__physical","status":"active","adm