[2026-02-18 07:52:04] [INFO] Product variant images has been updated - Shopidy ID - 10201317769530 - BC id=193 => {"product":{"id":10201317769530,"title":"4-20mA Type Vibration Sensor","body_html":"\u003Ch3\u003EMonitor the overall vibration of equipment\u003C\/h3\u003E\n\u003Cul\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003EMeasures vibrations from 0 to 25 RMS\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003ERequires a 24VDC power supply (FGD-0070)\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003EThe vibration sensor comes with two threaded adapters allowing it to screw into either: (a) 1\/4\"-28 UNF threaded hole, min. depth 13mm\u00a0\u00a0or\u00a0\u00a0(b) M8 threaded hole, min. depth 10mm\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003C\/ul\u003E\u003Cp style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003EThe Sensaphone Vibration Sensor will measure and provide real time vibration values to any Sensaphone that accepts a 4-20mA signal. When the vibration level falls outside of the Sensaphone\u2019s programmed high or low limit, the user will receive an alarm which displays or reads the current vibration value. Vibration on industrial equipment can be continuously monitored for unusual operating conditions and potential failure. The vibration sensor is designed to be permanently mounted on industrial equipment and continuously monitor the changes in a machine's vibration level. Detecting these changes early on prevents machinery from catastrophic failure, secondary damage, and expensive down time. The sensor comes with a 5m cable and is available with an optional magnetic mounting base. A 24V DC power supply is required to power the sensor.\u003C\/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E\u003C!-- pagebreak --\u003E\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/p\u003E\n\u003Ch3\u003E\u003Cspan\u003ETechnical Specifications\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/h3\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ECable Length:\u003C\/strong\u003E 16.4' | 5m\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EInput Circuit:\u003C\/strong\u003E 1 x analog 4-20mA\u00a0\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EMeasuring Range (mm\/s):\u003C\/strong\u003E 0 to 25 RMS\u00a0\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EFrequency Range (Hz):\u003C\/strong\u003E 10 to 1,000\u00a0\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EAmbient Temperature Range:\u003C\/strong\u003E -25\u00b0 to 80\u00b0C\u00a0\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EOperating Voltage:\u003C\/strong\u003E 9.6 to 32 DC\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ESensor Series:\u003C\/strong\u003E 4-20mA\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EProtection:\u003C\/strong\u003E IP 67 \/ IP 68 \/ IP 69K\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ENotes:\u003C\/strong\u003E Requires a 24VDC power supply (FGD-0070)\u003Cbr\u003EAvailable with optional magnetic mounting foot - FGD-0303-MOUNT\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EMounting Thread Size:\u003C\/strong\u003E The vibration sensor comes with two threaded adapters: (a) 1\/4\"-28 UNF threaded hole, min. depth 13mm\u003Cbr\u003EM8 threaded hole, min. depth 10mm\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/p\u003E\n\u003Ch3\u003E\u003Cspan\u003EDownloads\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/h3\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\u003Ca href=\"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0987\/4738\/4122\/files\/FGD-0303_CS.pdf\"\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E4-20mA Type Vibration Sensor Sales Brochure\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/a\u003E\u003C\/p\u003E","vendor":"Sensaphone","product_type":"physical","created_at":"2026-02-18T01:52:02-05:00","handle":"4-20ma-type-vibration-sensor","updated_at":"2026-02-18T01:52:02-05:00","published_at":"2026-02-18T01:51:59-05:00","template_suffix":null,"published_scope":"global","tags":"BRAND__Sensaphone, CAT__Other__VAL, OLD__193__ID, TYPE__physical","status":"active","admin_graphql_api_id":"gid:\/\/shopify\/Product\/10201317769530","variants":[{"id":53038673592634,"product_id":10201317769530,"title":"Magnetic","price":"419.00","position":1,"inventory_policy":"continue","compare_at_price":null,"option1":"Magnetic","option2":null,"option3":null,"created_at":"2026-02-18T01:52:02-05:00","updated_at":"2026-02-18T01:52:03-05:00","taxable":true,"barcode":"","fulfillment_service":"manual","grams"