[2026-02-18 07:52:42] [INFO] Product variant images has been updated - Shopidy ID - 10201318326586 - BC id=201 => {"product":{"id":10201318326586,"title":"VFC Refrigerator Temperature Sensor with Display","body_html":"\u003Ch3\u003EVFC Refrigerator Temperature Sensor with Display\u003C\/h3\u003E\n\u003Cul\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003EContinually monitors temperatures\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003EClearly displays the temperature\u00a0\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003EDisplays high and low temperatures\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003EProvides an audible alarm for out-of-range temperatures\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003ECan be programmed to turn on a light or siren for additional onsite alarm notifications\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003EMade in USA\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003C\/ul\u003E\u003Cp\u003EThe Temperature Sensor Display helps meet compliance when monitoring vaccines for the CDC\u2019s Vaccines For Children (VFC) program. From the factory, the display comes with a NIST certified temperature probe in a glass bead buffered bottle for installation inside of the refrigerator. The display is mounted to the outside of the refrigerator and then connected to a Sensaphone system that is capable of data logging.\u003C\/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003EUsers can read the refrigerator\u2019s temperature on a 2\u201d LCD display while the device passes the data along to the Sensaphone. Data can be viewed remotely, data logged, and monitored for high and low-temperature alarms.\u003C\/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003EThe Local Temperature Display also:\u003C\/p\u003E\n\u003Cul\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003EDisplays the highest and lowest temperatures\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003EProvides an audible alarm for out-of-range temperatures\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003ECan turn on a light or siren for additional onsite alarm notifications\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003C\/ul\u003E\u003Cp\u003EWhen the temperature falls out of the programmed high and low limits, the display triggers an audible alarm, immediately alerting onsite staff of a potential problem. This alarm is in addition to the alerts that the Sensaphone monitoring system sends to designated personnel when temperatures fall out of range.\u003C\/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003EThe display comes with a plug-in power supply and a battery that powers the device in the event of a power failure.\u003C\/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EItem includes:\u003C\/strong\u003E\u003C\/p\u003E\n\u003Cul\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003ETemperature display\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003ETemperature probe with 12\u2019 of wire\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003EBuffering bottle filled with glycol or glass beads\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003ENIST calibration certificate\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003EPower supply\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003ECoin cell batteries\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003EInstallation instructions\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003C\/ul\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C!-- pagebreak --\u003E\u003C\/p\u003E\n\u003Ch3\u003ETechnical Specifications\u003C\/h3\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EDimensions:\u003C\/strong\u003E 3.25 x 4.25 x 0.82\" | 8.25 x 10.8 x 2 cm\u00a0\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ETemperature Probe:\u003C\/strong\u003E 2.8K Thermistor\u00a0\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ETemperature Monitoring Range:\u003C\/strong\u003E \u003Cbr\u003EGlycol: -50\u00b0 to 50\u00b0C | -58\u00b0 to 122\u00b0F \u00a0\u003Cbr\u003EGlass Beads: -85\u00b0 to 80\u00b0C | -121\u00b0 to 176\u00b0F\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EWeight:\u003C\/strong\u003E 0.25lb | 114gm\u00a0\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EAccuracy:\u003C\/strong\u003E 1\u00b0F | 0.5\u00b0C\u00a0\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EPower:\u003C\/strong\u003E 12VDC\u00a0\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EBattery:\u003C\/strong\u003E (2) CR2450 lithium coin cells (included)\u00a0\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EMaterial:\u003C\/strong\u003E ABS plastic\u00a0\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EMounting:\u003C\/strong\u003E 3M Dual Lock Reclosable Fasteners\u00a0\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EDisplay Size:\u003C\/strong\u003E 1.4 x 2.0\" LCD\u00a0\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EAlarm Output:\u003C\/strong\u003E Solid state alarm output (Open Drain) rated 12VDC 250mA\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ESensaphone Output:\u003C\/strong\u003E Current regulated output that simulates a 2.8K thermistor. For connecting to any Sensaphone that accepts 2.8K thermistors.\u00a0\u003C\/p\u003E\n\u003Ch3\u003EDownloads\u003C\/h3\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\u003Ca href=\"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0987\/4738\/4122\/files\/LIT-0208_TemperatureDisplay_Instructions.pdf\"\u003EVFC Refrigerator Temperature Sensor with Display Instructions \u003C\/a\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Ca href=\"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0987\/4738\/4122\/files\/FGD-0120-VFC_CS.pdf\"\u003EVFC Refrigerator Temperature Sensor with Display Cutsheet\u003C\/a\u003E\u003C\/p\u003E","vendor":"Sensaphone","product_type":"physical","created_at":"2026-02-18T01:52:40-05:00","handle":"vfc-refrigerator-temperature-sensor-with-display","updated_at":"2026-02-18T01:52:41-05:00","published_at":"2026-02-18T01:52:28-05:00","template_suffix":null,"published_scope":"global","tags":"BRAND__Sensaphone, CAT__Temperature Sensors__VAL, OLD__201__ID, TYPE__physical","status":"active","admin_graphql_api_id":"gid:\/\/shopify\/Product\/10201318326586","variants":[{"id":53038675493178,"product_id":10201318326586,"title":"Glass Bead Bottle","price":"249.99","position":1,"inventory_policy":"continue","compare_at_price":null,"option1":"Glass Bead Bottle","option2":null,"option3":null,"created_at":"2026-02-18T01:52:41-05:00","updated_at":"2026-02-18T01:52:41-05:00","taxable":true,"barcode":"","fulfillment_service":"manual","grams":0,"inventory_management":"shopify","requires_shipping":true,"sku":"FGD-VFC-GBV","weight":0,"weight_unit":"lb","inventory_item_id":55065779700026,"inventory_quantity":0,"old_inventory_quantity":0,"admin_graphql_api_id":"gid:\/\/shopify\/ProductVariant\/53038675493178","image_id":55073524384058},{"id":53038675525946,"product_i