[2026-02-18 07:52:51] [INFO] Product variant images has been updated - Shopidy ID - 10201318424890 - BC id=204 => {"product":{"id":10201318424890,"title":"WSG Wireless Room Temperature Sensor","body_html":"\u003Ch3\u003EWirelessly Monitor Room Temperature\u003C\/h3\u003E\n\u003Cul\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003EMeasures temperature from -20\u00b0 to 115\u00b0F | -28\u00b0 to 46\u00b0C\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003EAccurate to \u00b1 1\u00b0F |\u00a0 \u00b1 .56\u00b0C\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003ECommunicates wirelessly with WSG30 base unit up to 300\u2019 away\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003EIncludes two AA batteries\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003EOptional power supply available\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003C\/ul\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan\u003EThe Wireless Room Temperature Sensor is used exclusively with the WSG30 system to measure ambient air temperature wherever the sensor is installed. When the temperature falls outside of the WSG30 system\u2019s programmed high or low limit, the user will receive an alarm via text message or email. The sensor includes two AA alkaline batteries which will power the sensor for up to two years. An optional plug-in power supply is also available, in which case the batteries then become a backup if the main AC power fails. The wireless sensor can be placed up to 300\u2019 away from the WSG30 or further if multiple sensors are used to create a mesh network.\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E\u003C!-- pagebreak --\u003E\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/p\u003E\n\u003Ch3\u003E\u003Cspan\u003ETechnical Specifications\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/h3\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ESensor Temperature Range:\u003C\/strong\u003E 32\u00b0 to 115\u00b0F | 0\u00b0 to 57\u00b0C\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EAccuracy:\u003C\/strong\u003E 1\u00b0F | .56\u00b0C\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EWireless Range:\u003C\/strong\u003E 300' | 90m\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EConnection:\u003C\/strong\u003E Wireless\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EDimensions:\u003C\/strong\u003E 3.1 x 3.9 x 1.1\" | 79 x 99 x 28mm\u00a0\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ESensor Series:\u003C\/strong\u003E WSG Wireless\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EDownloads:\u003C\/strong\u003E\u003C\/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\u003Ca href=\"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0987\/4738\/4122\/files\/CS_FGD-WSG30-TMP.pdf\"\u003E\u003Cspan\u003EWSG Wireless Room Temperature Sensor Cutsheet\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/a\u003E\u003C\/p\u003E","vendor":"Sensaphone","product_type":"physical","created_at":"2026-02-18T01:52:50-05:00","handle":"wsg-wireless-room-temperature-sensor","updated_at":"2026-02-18T01:52:50-05:00","published_at":"2026-02-18T01:52:48-05:00","template_suffix":null,"published_scope":"global","tags":"BRAND__Sensaphone, CAT__Temperature Sensors__VAL, CAT__Wireless__VAL, OLD__204__ID, TYPE__physical","status":"active","admin_graphql_api_id":"gid:\/\/shopify\/Product\/10201318424890","variants":[{"id":53038675919162,"product_id":10201318424890,"title":"Clear Door","price":"239.00","position":1,"inventory_policy":"continue","compare_at_price":null,"option1":"Clear Door","option2":null,"option3":null,"created_at":"2026-02-18T01:52:50-05:00","updated_at":"2026-02-18T01:52:50-05:00","taxable":true,"barcode":"","fulfillment_service":"manual","grams":0,"inventory_management":"shopify","requires_shipping":true,"sku":"FGD-WSG30-TMP, FGD-WSG30-SENCD","weight":0,"weight_unit":"lb","inventory_item_id":55065780126010,"inventory_quantity":0,"old_inventory_quantity":0,"admin_graphql_api_id":"gid:\/\/shopify\/ProductVariant\/53038675919162","image_id":null},{"id":53038675951930,"product_id":10201318424890,"title":"None","price":"189.00","position":2,"inventory_policy":"continue","compare_at_price":null,"option1":"None","option2":null,"option3":null,"created_at":"2026-02-18T01:52:50-05:00","updated_at":"2026-02-18T01:52:50-05:00","taxable":true,"barcode":"","fulfillment_serv