[2026-02-18 07:53:06] [INFO] Product variant images has been updated - Shopidy ID - 10201318719802 - BC id=205 => {"product":{"id":10201318719802,"title":"WSG Wireless Temperature Sensor w\/ External Probe","body_html":"\u003Ch4\u003EMonitor temperatures inside a refrigerator, freezer or other harsh environment\u003C\/h4\u003E\n\u003Cul\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003EThe sensor's external temperature probe can be installed in a refrigerator, freezer or other harsh environment, while the sensor circuitry remains in a clean dry environment\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003EChoose between two temperature ranges; -20\u00b0 to 115\u00b0F or -121\u00b0 to 115\u00b0F\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003EAccurate to \u00b1 1\u00b0F |\u00a0 \u00b1 .56\u00b0C\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003EIncludes two AA batteries\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003EOptional power supply available\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003C\/ul\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan\u003EWSG Wireless Temperature Sensors with External Probes are designed to work exclusively with the Sensaphone WSG30. This sensor circuitry includes a built-in radio transmitter. The \u003C\/span\u003Esensors attach to a remote temperature probe\u003Cspan\u003E so that temperature measurements can be made in a refrigerator, freezer or other harsh environments. The sensor is available in two temperature ranges; -20\u00b0 to 115\u00b0F or -121\u00b0 to 115\u00b0F. It comes with two AA alkaline batteries which will power the sensor for up to two years. An optional plug-in power supply is also available in which case the batteries become a backup if the main AC power fails.\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E\u003C!-- pagebreak --\u003E\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/p\u003E\n\u003Ch4\u003E\u003Cspan\u003ETechnical Specifications\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/h4\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ESensor Temperature Range:\u003C\/strong\u003E -121\u00b0 to 115\u00b0F | -85\u00b0 to 57\u00b0C or -20\u00b0 to 115\u00b0F | -28\u00b0 to 46\u00b0C\u00a0\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EAccuracy:\u003C\/strong\u003E 1\u00b0F | .56\u00b0C\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EWireless Range:\u003C\/strong\u003E 300' | 90m\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EConnection:\u003C\/strong\u003E Wireless\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EHousing:\u003C\/strong\u003E Plastic\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EDimensions:\u003C\/strong\u003E 3.1 x 3.9 x 1.1\" | 79 x 99 x 28mm\u00a0\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ESensor Series:\u003C\/strong\u003E WSG Wireless\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan\u003EDownloads:\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\u003Ca href=\"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0987\/4738\/4122\/files\/CS_FGD-WSG30-TEX.pdf\"\u003EWSG Wireless Temperature Sensor w\/ External Probe Cutsheet\u003C\/a\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Ca href=\"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0987\/4738\/4122\/files\/CS_FGD-WSG30-TEX85.pdf\"\u003EWSG Wireless Ultra Low Temperature Sensor w\/ External Probe Cutsheet\u003C\/a\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003C\/p\u003E","vendor":"Sensaphone","product_type":"physical","created_at":"2026-02-18T01:53:04-05:00","handle":"wsg-wireless-temperature-sensor-w-external-probe","updated_at":"2026-02-18T01:53:05-05:00","published_at":"2026-02-18T01:52:56-05:00","template_suffix":null,"published_scope":"global","tags":"BRAND__Sensaphone, CAT__Temperature Sensors__VAL, CAT__Wireless__VAL, OLD__205__ID, TYPE__physical","status":"active","admin_graphql_api_id":"gid:\/\/shopify\/Product\/10201318719802","variants":[{"id":53038677164346,"product_id":10201318719802,"title":"NIST Calibration \/ Ultra Low Temperature Probe (-121\u00b0 to 115)","price":"319.00","position":1,"inventory_policy":"continue","compare_at_price":null,"option1":"NIST Calibration","option2":"Ultra Low Temperature Probe (-121\u00b0 to 115)","option3":null,"created_at":"2026-02-18T01:53:04-05:00","updated_at":"2026-02-18T01:53:05-05:00","taxable":true,"barcode":"","fulfillment_service":"manual","g