[2026-02-18 07:53:29] [INFO] Product variant images has been updated - Shopidy ID - 10201318916410 - BC id=213 => {"product":{"id":10201318916410,"title":"WSG Wireless Temperature Sensor with RTD Probe","body_html":"\u003Ch3\u003EMeasure Extreme Temperatures\u003C\/h3\u003E\n\u003Cul\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003EMeasures temperature from -328\u00b0 to 248\u00b0F | -200\u00b0 to 120\u00b0C\u00a0\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003ETwo size probes to choose from: 1\" or 14\"\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003EProbes include 10' of wire\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003ECommunicates wirelessly with WSG30 base unit up to 300\u2019 away\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003EIncludes two AA batteries\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003EOptional power supply available\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003C\/ul\u003E\u003Cp\u003EThe Wireless Temperature Sensor with RTD Probe is used exclusively with the WSG30 system. It measures extreme air temperature in applications where traditional sensors will fail. The sensor is available with two different\u00a0sized temperature sensing probes: \u003Cspan\u003E1\" or 14\"\u003C\/span\u003E. The 14\u201d probe is recommended for applications where the sensor cabling cannot be exposed to the cold atmosphere such as monitoring liquid nitrogen. Both probes come with 10\u2019 of wire.\u003C\/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003EWhen the temperature falls outside of the WSG30 system\u2019s programmed high or low limit, the user will receive an alarm via text message or email. The sensor includes two AA lithium batteries which will power the sensor for up to two years. An optional plug-in power supply is also available, so the batteries serve as a backup if the main AC power fails. The wireless sensor can be placed up to 300\u2019 away from the WSG30 or further if multiple sensors are used to create a mesh network.\u003C\/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\u003C!-- pagebreak --\u003E\u003C\/p\u003E\n\u003Ch4\u003ETechnical Specifications\u003C\/h4\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ESensor Temperature Range:\u003C\/strong\u003E -328\u00b0 to 248\u00b0F | -200\u00b0 to 120\u00b0C\u00a0\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ERTD Element:\u003C\/strong\u003E PT100 - 385 ALPHA - CLASS - B\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EWireless Range:\u003C\/strong\u003E 300' | 90m\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EConnection:\u003C\/strong\u003E Wireless\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EHousing:\u003C\/strong\u003E Plastic\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EDimensions:\u003C\/strong\u003E 3.1 x 3.9 x 1.1\" | 79 x 99 x 28mm\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ENotes:\u003C\/strong\u003E Element tolerance to IEC 60751 edition 2.0, par 5.1.2\u003C\/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003EDownloads:\u003C\/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\u003Ca href=\"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0987\/4738\/4122\/files\/FGD-WSG30-RTD_CS.pdf\"\u003EWSG Wireless Temperature Sensor with RTD Probe Cutsheet\u003C\/a\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Ca href=\"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0987\/4738\/4122\/files\/LIT-0215_RTDinstructions.pdf\"\u003EWSG Wireless Temperature Sensor with RTD Probe Instructions\u003C\/a\u003E\u003C\/p\u003E","vendor":"Sensaphone","product_type":"physical","created_at":"2026-02-18T01:53:27-05:00","handle":"wsg-wireless-temperature-sensor-with-rtd-probe","updated_at":"2026-02-18T01:53:27-05:00","published_at":"2026-02-18T01:53:26-05:00","template_suffix":null,"published_scope":"global","tags":"BRAND__Sensaphone, CAT__Temperature Sensors__VAL, CAT__Wireless__VAL, OLD__213__ID, TYPE__physical","status":"active","admin_graphql_api_id":"gid:\/\/shopify\/Product\/10201318916410","variants":[{"id":53038678212922,"product_id":10201318916410,"title":"14\" RTD Probe","price":"349.00","position":1,"inventory_policy":"continue","compare_at_price":null,"option1":"14\" RTD Probe","option2":null,"option3":null,"created_at":"2026-02-18T01:53:27-05:00","updated_at":"2026-02-18T01:53:28-05:00","taxable":true,"barcode":"","fulfillment_service":"manual","grams":0,"inventory_management":"shopify","requires_shipping":true,"sku":"FGD-WSG30-RTD14","