[2026-02-18 07:53:36] [INFO] Product variant images has been updated - Shopidy ID - 10201318981946 - BC id=216 => {"product":{"id":10201318981946,"title":"WSG Wireless Humidity Sensor","body_html":"\u003Ch3\u003EMonitor humidity levels\u003C\/h3\u003E\n\u003Cul\u003E\n\u003Cli style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003EMeasures humidity from 0 to 95%\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003E3% accuracy from 20 to 80%, \u00b15% otherwise\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003ECommunicates wirelessly with WSG30 base unit up to 300\u2019 away\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003EIncludes two AA batteries\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003EOptional power supply available\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003C\/ul\u003E\u003Cp style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003EThe Wireless Humidity Sensor is used exclusively with the WSG30 system to measure humidity. When the humidity level falls outside of the WSG30 system\u2019s programmed high or low limit, the user will receive an alarm via text message or email which displays the current humidity level. The sensor can be programed to detect humidity levels from 0 to 95% RH. It is ideal for clean indoor applications such as a home, office, museum or hospital. The sensor includes two AA alkaline batteries which will power the sensor for up to two years. An optional plug-in power supply is also available, in which case the batteries then become a backup if the main AC power fails. The wireless sensor can be placed up to 300\u2019 away from the WSG30 or further if multiple sensors are used to create a mesh network.\u003C\/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E\u003C!-- pagebreak --\u003E\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/p\u003E\n\u003Ch3\u003E\u003Cspan\u003ETechnical Specifications\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/h3\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EOperating Temperature:\u003C\/strong\u003E 32\u00b0 to 122\u00b0F | 0\u00b0 to 50\u00b0C\u00a0\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003E