[2026-02-18 07:53:48] [INFO] Product variant images has been updated - Shopidy ID - 10201319145786 - BC id=218 => {"product":{"id":10201319145786,"title":"WSG Wireless Power Failure Sensor","body_html":"\u003Ch3\u003EMonitor for power loss\u003C\/h3\u003E\n\u003Cul\u003E\n\u003Cli style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003E\u003Cspan\u003ESimply plug this sensor in to any outlet (110 volt AC) circuit needing to be monitored\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003ESends WSG30 into alarm when power is lost\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003ECommunicates wirelessly with WSG30 base unit up to 300\u2019 away\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003EIncludes 5V power supply\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003EIncludes 2 AA batteries which power the sensor in the event of a power failure\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003C\/ul\u003E\u003Cp style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003EThe Wireless Power Failure Sensor is used exclusively with the WSG30 system to monitor for the loss of power wherever it is plugged in. When the sensor detects power failure, it will wirelessly communicate the failure back to the WSG30. Users will receive an alarm via text message or email. The sensor can be plugged into any 110 volt AC outlet. It requires no additional power for operation. The sensor includes two AA alkaline batteries which will power the sensor during a main power failure. The wireless sensor can be placed up to 300\u2019 away from the WSG30 or further if multiple sensors are used to create a mesh network.\u003C\/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E\u003C!-- pagebreak --\u003E\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/p\u003E\n\u003Ch3\u003E\u003Cspan\u003ETechnical Specifications\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/h3\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EOperating Temperature:\u003C\/strong\u003E 32\u00b0 to 122\u00b0F | 0\u00b0 to 50\u00b0C\u00a0\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EWireless Range:\u003C\/strong\u003E 300' | 90m\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EConnection:\u003C\/strong\u003E Wireless\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EHousing:\u003C\/strong\u003E Plastic\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EDimensions:\u003C\/strong\u003E 3.1 x 3.9 x 1.1\" | 79 x 99 x 28mm\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ESensor Series:\u003C\/strong\u003E WSG Wireless\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/p\u003E\n\u003Ch3\u003E\u003Cspan\u003EDownloads\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/h3\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\u003Ca href=\"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0987\/4738\/4122\/files\/CS_FGD-WSG30-PWR.pdf\"\u003E\u003Cspan\u003EWSG Wireless Power Failure Sensor Sales Brochure\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/a\u003E\u003C\/p\u003E","vendor":"Sensaphone","product_type":"physical","created_at":"2026-02-18T01:53:47-05:00","handle":"wsg-wireless-power-failure-sensor","updated_at":"2026-02-18T01:53:47-05:00","published_at":"2026-02-18T01:53:45-05:00","template_suffix":null,"published_scope":"global","tags":"BRAND__Sensaphone, CAT__Power Sensors__VAL, CAT__Wireless__VAL, OLD__218__ID, TYPE__physical","status":"active","admin_graphql_api_id":"gid:\/\/shopify\/Product\/10201319145786","variants":[{"id":53038679163194,"product_id":10201319145786,"title":"Clear Door","price":"249.00","position":1,"inventory_policy":"continue","compare_at_price":null,"option1":"Clear Door","option2":null,"option3":null,"created_at":"2026-02-18T01:53:47-05:00","updated_at":"2026-02-18T01:53:47-05:00","taxable":true,"barcode":"","fulfillment_service":"manual","grams":0,"inventory_management":"shopify","requires_shipping":true,"sku":"FGD-WSG30-PWR, FGD-WSG30-PWR","weight":0,"weight_unit":"lb","inventory_item_id":55065783370042,"inventory_quantity":0,"old_inventory_quantity":0,"admin_graphql_api_id":"gid:\/\/shopify\/ProductVariant\/53038679163194","image_id":null},{"id":53038679195962,"product_id":10201319145786,"title":"None","price":"199.00","position":2,"inventory_policy":"continue","compare_at_price":null,"option1":"None","option2":null,"option3":null,"created_at