[2026-02-18 07:53:55] [INFO] Product variant images has been updated - Shopidy ID - 10201319244090 - BC id=219 => {"product":{"id":10201319244090,"title":"WSG Wireless 4-20mA Interface","body_html":"\u003Ch3\u003EMonitor the output of any 4-20mA transducer\u003C\/h3\u003E\n\u003Cul\u003E\n\u003Cli style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003EInterfaces with any 4-20mA transducer\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003ECommunicates contact data wirelessly with WSG30 base unit up to 300\u2019 away\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003EIncludes three AA batteries\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003EInterface provides up to 30mA of current to power 4-20mA transducer\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003C\/ul\u003E\u003Cp style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003EThe Wireless 4-20mA Interface is used exclusively with the WSG30 system to interface with any transducer that outputs a 4-20mA signal. The interface will measure and provide real time values to to the WSG30. When the level falls outside of the WSG30\u2019s programmed high or low limit, the user will receive an alarm which displays the current value.\u003C\/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003E\u003Cspan style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003EThe Wireless 4-20mA interface has an internal 24 VDC power supply that is intended to be used to power the 4-20mA transducer. It can provide up to 30mA of current. \u003C\/span\u003E\u003Cspan style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003EThe interface includes three AA alkaline batteries which will power the interface and sensor during a power failure. The wireless interface can be placed up to 300\u2019 away from the WSG30 or further if multiple sensors are used to create a mesh network\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E\u003C!-- pagebreak --\u003E\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/p\u003E\n\u003Ch3\u003E\u003Cspan\u003ETechnical Specifications\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/h3\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EOperating Temperature:\u003C\/strong\u003E 32\u00b0 to 122\u00b0F | 0\u00b0 to 50\u00b0C\u00a0\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EWireless Range:\u003C\/strong\u003E 300' | 90m\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EConnection:\u003C\/strong\u003E Wireless\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EHousing:\u003C\/strong\u003E Platics\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EDimensions:\u003C\/strong\u003E 6.8 x 3.5 x 1.6\" | 173 x 89 x 40mm\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ESensor Series:\u003C\/strong\u003E WSG Wirelss\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/p\u003E\n\u003Ch3\u003E\u003Cspan\u003EDownloads\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/h3\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\u003Ca href=\"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0987\/4738\/4122\/files\/CS_FGD-WSG30-4-20.pdf\"\u003E\u003Cspan\u003EWSG Wireless 4-20mA Interface Sales Brochure\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/a\u003E\u003C\/p\u003E","vendor":"Sensaphone","product_type":"physical","created_at":"2026-02-18T01:53:54-05:00","handle":"wsg-wireless-4-20ma-interface","updated_at":"2026-02-18T01:53:54-05:00","published_at":"2026-02-18T01:53:51-05:00","template_suffix":null,"published_scope":"global","tags":"BRAND__Sensaphone, CAT__Wireless__VAL, MAINSKU__FGD-WSG30-4-20, OLD__219__ID, TYPE__physical","status":"active","admin_graphql_api_id":"gid:\/\/shopify\/Product\/10201319244090","variants":[{"id":53038679523642,"product_id":10201319244090,"title":"Default Title","price":"259.00","position":1,"inventory_policy":"continue","compare_at_price":null,"option1":"Default Title","option2":null,"option3":null,"created_at":"2026-02-18T01:53:54-05:00","updated_at":"2026-02-18T01:53:55-05:00","taxable":true,"barcode":"","fulfillment_service":"manual","grams":0,"inventory_management":"shopify","requires_shipping":true,"sku":"FGD-WSG30-4-20","weight":0,"weight_unit":"lb","inventory_item_id":55065783730490,"inventory_quantity":0,"old_inventory_quantity":0,"admin_graphql_api_id":"gid:\/\/shopify\/ProductVariant\/53038679523642","image_id":null}],"options":[{"id":12742211076410,"product_id":10201319244090,"name":"Title","position":1,"values":["Default Title"]}],"images":[{"id":55073530609978,"alt":"219_main_image_0","position":1,"product_id":10201319244090,"created_at":"2026-02-18T01:53:54-05:00","updated_at":"2026-02-18T01:53:54-05:00","admin_graphql_api_id":"gid:\/\/shopify\/MediaImage\/45112718262586","width":1000,"height":1000,"src":"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0987\/4738\/4122\/files\/PH_WSG30-4-20_WEB__18251.jpg?v=1771397634","variant_ids":[]},{"id":55073530642746,"alt":"-","position":2,"product_id":10201319244090,"created_at":"2026-02-18T01:53:54-05:00","updated_at":"2026-02-18T01:53:54-05:00","admin_graphql_api_id":"gid:\/\/shopify\/MediaImage\/45112718295354","width":386,"height":386,"src":"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0987\/4738\/4122\/files\/PH_WSG30-4-20_WEB__18251.1708959836.386.513.jpg?v=1771397634","variant_ids":[]}],"image":{"id":55073530609978,"alt":"219_main_image_0","position":1,"product_id":10201319244090,"created_at":"2026-02-18T01:53:54-05:00","updated_at":"2026-02-18T01:53:54-05:00","admin_graphql_api_id":"gid:\/\/shopify\/MediaImage\/45112718262586","width":1000,"height":1000,"src":"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0987\/4738\/4122\/files\/PH_WSG30-4-20_WEB__18251.jpg?v=1771397634","variant_ids":[]}}}
