[2026-02-18 07:54:07] [INFO] Product variant images has been updated - Shopidy ID - 10201319375162 - BC id=220 => {"product":{"id":10201319375162,"title":"WSG Wireless Water Detection Sensors","body_html":"\u003Ch3\u003EMonitor for the presence of water\u003C\/h3\u003E\n\u003Cul\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003ESensors detect the presence of water in a small or large area\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003EAA batteries power sensor for up to two years\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003C\/ul\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan\u003EThe WSG30 Wireless Water Detection Sensors are designed to work exclusively with the Sensaphone WSG30. These sensors include a built-in radio transmitter and water sensing probes for monitoring for the presence of water. The Spot Water Detection sensor will monitor for the presence of water directly under the sensor. The Zone Water Detection sensor connects to a water sensing rope which provides up to 10' of coverage. Up to nine additional lengths of water rope can be added to extend the monitoring area.\u00a0 The sensors comes with three AA alkaline batteries which will power the sensor for up to two years. \u003C\/span\u003E\u003Cspan\u003EAn optional plug-in power supply is also available, in which case the batteries then become a backup if the main AC power fails. The wireless sensor can be placed up to 300\u2019 away from the WSG30 or further if multiple sensors are used to create a mesh network. To install, simply lay the sensor on the floor wherever it is suspected water will collect.\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E\u003C!-- pagebreak --\u003E\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/p\u003E\n\u003Ch3\u003E\u003Cspan\u003ETechnical Specifications\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/h3\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EOperating Temperature:\u003C\/strong\u003E 32\u00b0 to 122\u00b0F | 0\u00b0 to 50\u00b0C\u00a0\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EWireless Range:\u003C\/strong\u003E 300' | 90m\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EConnection:\u003C\/strong\u003E Wireless\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EHousing:\u003C\/strong\u003E Plastic\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EDimensions:\u003C\/strong\u003E 6.8 x 3.5 x 1.6\" | 173 x 89 x 40mm\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ESensor Series:\u003C\/strong\u003E WSG Series\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EDownloads\u003C\/strong\u003E:\u003Cbr\u003E\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E\u003Ca href=\"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0987\/4738\/4122\/files\/CS_FGD-WSG30-ZONE.pdf\"\u003EWSG Wireless Zone Water Detection Sensor Cutsheet\u003C\/a\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003C\/span\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E\u003Ca href=\"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0987\/4738\/4122\/files\/CS_FGD-WSG30-SPOT.pdf\"\u003EWSG Wireless Spot Water Detection Sensor Cutsheet\u003C\/a\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/p\u003E","vendor":"Sensaphone","product_type":"physical","created_at":"2026-02-18T01:54:05-05:00","handle":"wsg-wireless-water-detection-sensors","updated_at":"2026-02-18T01:54:06-05:00","published_at":"2026-02-18T01:54:00-05:00","template_suffix":null,"published_scope":"global","tags":"BRAND__Sensaphone, CAT__Water Detection__VAL, CAT__Wireless__VAL, OLD__220__ID, TYPE__physical","status":"active","admin_graphql_api_id":"gid:\/\/shopify\/Product\/10201319375162","variants":[{"id":53038680146234,"product_id":10201319375162,"title":"Spot Water Detection Sensor","price":"249.00","position":1,"inventory_policy":"continue","compare_at_price":null,"option1":"Spot Water Detection Sensor","option2":null,"option3":null,"created_at":"2026-02-18T01:54:06-05:00","updated_at":"2026-02-18T01:54:06-05:00","taxable":true,"barcode":"","fulfillment_service":"manual","grams":0,"inventory_management":"shopify","requires_shipping":true,"sku":"FGD-WSG30-SPOT","weight":0,"weight_unit":"lb","inventory_item_id":55065784353082,"inventory_quantity":0,"old_inventory_quantity":0,"admin_graphql_api_id":"gid:\/\/shopify\/Product