[2026-02-18 07:54:29] [INFO] Product variant images has been updated - Shopidy ID - 10201319604538 - BC id=226 => {"product":{"id":10201319604538,"title":"IMS-4000 Enterprise Monitoring Node Expansion Unit","body_html":"\u003Ch3\u003EExpand the capabilities of your IMS-4000E system\u003C\/h3\u003E\n\u003Cul\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003EAllows expansion of IMS-4000E system\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003EUp to eight sensors per Node\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003EUp to 31 Nodes can be associated with each IMS-4000E Host\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003ECan be rack or desktop mounted\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003C\/ul\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan\u003EThe IMS-4000E Node allows IMS-4000E users to expand their infrastructure and monitor additional inputs in locations away from the IMS-4000E Host. Up to thirty-one Nodes can be used with each IMS-4000E Host. Much like the Host, the Node can monitor eight inputs for environmental conditions and or alarm contacts from other computer equipment such as UPS systems. The Node connects to the Host via a RJ-45 10\/100BASE-T Ethernet and is monitored via the ConsoleView software included with the Host.\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E\u003C!-- pagebreak --\u003E\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ECommunication Method:\u003C\/strong\u003E Ethernet and\/or phone via IMS-4000 Host\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ENumber of Inputs:\u003C\/strong\u003E 8\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EInput Types:\u003C\/strong\u003E IMS Solutions\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ERemote Access:\u003C\/strong\u003E ConsoleView software and or website to access status and programming\u00a0\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ELocal Access:\u003C\/strong\u003E LEDs to show ethernet connectivity, and power alarms\u00a0\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EPower Supply:\u003C\/strong\u003E Plug in power supply also monitors for power failures. Built in battery backup\u00a0\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EPhysical:\u003C\/strong\u003E 9.6 x 1.75 x 7\" | 244 x 44 x 178mm\u00a0\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EWarranty:\u003C\/strong\u003E 3 Years\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EStandards:\u003C\/strong\u003E FCC Part 15 Class A, USA Emission Standards\u003Cbr\u003EFCC Part 68 (47 C.F.R. Part 68), USA Telecommunications Standards\u003Cbr\u003EUL60950\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003C\/span\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/p\u003E","vendor":"Sensaphone","product_type":"physical","created_at":"2026-02-18T01:54:27-05:00","handle":"ims-4000-enterprise-monitoring-node-expansion-unit","updated_at":"2026-02-18T01:54:28-05:00","published_at":"2026-02-18T01:54:21-05:00","template_suffix":null,"published_scope":"global","tags":"BRAND__Sensaphone, CAT__Accessories__VAL, OLD__226__ID, TYPE__physical","status":"active","admin_graphql_api_id":"gid:\/\/shopify\/Product\/10201319604538","variants":[{"id":53038681030970,"product_id":10201319604538,"title":"Standard Power","price":"839.00","position":1,"inventory_policy":"continue","compare_at_price":null,"option1":"Standard Power","option2":null,"option3":null,"created_at":"2026-02-18T01:54:27-05:00","updated_at":"2026-02-18T01:54:28-05:00","taxable":true,"barcode":"","fulfillment_service":"manual","grams":0,"inventory_management":"shopify","requires_shipping":true,"sku":"IMS-4002E","weight":0,"weight_unit":"lb","inventory_item_id":55065785237818,"inventory_quantity":0,"old_inventory_quantity":0,"admin_graphql_api_id":"gid:\/\/shopify\/ProductVariant\/53038681030970","image_id":null},{"id":53038681063738,"product_id":10201319604538,"title":"International Power Adapter Kit","price":"889.00","position":2,"inventory_policy":"continue","compare_at_price":null,"option1":"International Power Adapter Kit","option2":null,"option3":null,"created_at":"2026-02-18T01:54:27-05:00","updated_at":"2026-02-18T01:54:28-05:00","taxable":true,"barcode":"","fulfillment_service":"manual","grams":0,"inventory_management":"shopify","requires_shipping":true,"s