[2026-02-18 07:54:39] [INFO] Product variant images has been updated - Shopidy ID - 10201319768378 - BC id=228 => {"product":{"id":10201319768378,"title":"IMS-4000 Dual Relay Output Module","body_html":"\u003Ch3\u003EControl two devices from any IMS-4000E Host or Node\u003C\/h3\u003E\n\u003Cul\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003EThe module connects to an IMS-4000 Host or Node to receive its control instructions.\u003C\/p\u003E\n\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003EConnects to IMS-4000E Host or Node using included using the 9-pin null modem cable\u003C\/p\u003E\n\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003C\/ul\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan\u003EThe IMS-4310E Dual Relay Output Module allows you to control two devices from any IMS-4000E Host or Node. Each output may be controlled either manually or automatically. Each output has the option of providing either a dry relay contact or 12VDC power. Two switches located inside the device select the output type.\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003EThe IMS-4000E allows you to program an Alarm Response whenever an environmental or IP Alarm occurs. An Alarm Response is an action that occurs automatically whenever an alarm occurs. Using the Relay Module you can automatically turn On, Off, or Cycle equipment whenever an Environmental or IP alarm occurs.\u003C\/p\u003E","vendor":"Sensaphone","product_type":"physical","created_at":"2026-02-18T01:54:37-05:00","handle":"ims-4000-dual-relay-output-module","updated_at":"2026-02-18T01:54:38-05:00","published_at":"2026-02-18T01:54:30-05:00","template_suffix":null,"published_scope":"global","tags":"BRAND__Sensaphone, CAT__Other__VAL, MAINSKU__IMS-4310E, OLD__228__ID, TYPE__physical","status":"active","admin_graphql_api_id":"gid:\/\/shopify\/Product\/10201319768378","variants":[{"id":53038681719098,"product_id":10201319768378,"title":"Default Title","price":"0.00","position":1,"inventory_policy":"continue","compare_at_price":null,"option1":"Default Title","option2":null,"option3":null,"cre