[2026-02-18 07:55:29] [INFO] Product variant images has been updated - Shopidy ID - 10201320292666 - BC id=237 => {"product":{"id":10201320292666,"title":"IMS Solution Indoor Temperature Sensors","body_html":"\u003Ch3\u003EEasy temperature monitoring\u003C\/h3\u003E\n\u003Cul\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003EConnects to the IMS system via RJ-45 patch cable (not included)\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003EChoose between sensors that have a local LCD display or no display\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003ESensors with display measure temperatures from 32\u00b0 to 95\u00b0F\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003ESensors without display measure temperatures from 5\u00b0 to 140\u00b0F\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003C\/ul\u003E\u003Cp style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003EThe IMS Room Temperature Sensors are used exclusively with the Sensaphone IMS system to measure and provide real time indoor air temperatures from 5\u00b0 to 140\u00b0F or 32\u00b0 to 95\u00b0F. The system will go into alarm when the temperature falls outside of the programmed high or low limit. The sensor comes in an attractive white plastic enclosure that can be mounted to a single gang electrical box or directly to the wall. The connection from the sensor to the IMS system can use your existing network wiring infrastructure, which allows the sensor to be installed in location away from the IMS host device.\u003Cspan\u003E\u00a0Choose between a local display with values displayed in \u00b0F, \u00b0C or no local display.\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E\u003C!-- pagebreak --\u003E\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/p\u003E\n\u003Ch4\u003E\u003Cspan\u003ETechnical Specifications:\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/h4\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ESensor Temperature Range:\u003C\/strong\u003E \u003Cbr\u003E\u003C\/span\u003E\u003Cspan\u003EIMS-4810E: 5\u00b0 to 122\u00b0F\u003Cbr\u003EIMS-4810E-C: -15\u00b0 to 50\u00b0C\u00a0\u003Cbr\u003EIMS-4811E: 32\u00b0 to 95\u00b0F\u003Cbr\u003EIMS-4813E: 0\u00b0 to 35\u00b0C\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EAccuracy:\u003C\/strong\u003E 3\u00b0F | 1.7\u00b0C\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EConnection:\u003C\/strong\u003E RJ45\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EDimensions:\u003C\/strong\u003E 4.5 x 2.8 x 1.3\" | 110 x 70 x 30mm\u00a0\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ESensor Series:\u003C\/strong\u003E IMS Solution\u003Cbr\u003E\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/p\u003E\n\u003Ch3\u003E\u003Cspan\u003EDownloads\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/h3\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E\u003Ca href=\"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0987\/4738\/4122\/files\/CS_IMS-4810E.pdf\"\u003EIMS Solution Room Temperature Sensor Sales Brochure (IMS-4810E)\u003C\/a\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Ca href=\"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0987\/4738\/4122\/files\/CS_IMS-4811E.pdf\"\u003EIMS Solution Room Temperature Sensor \u00b0F Sales Brochure (IMS-4811E)\u003C\/a\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Ca href=\"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0987\/4738\/4122\/files\/CS_IMS-4813E.pdf\"\u003EIMS Solution Room Temperature Sensor \u00b0C Sales Brochure IMS-4813E)\u003C\/a\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/p\u003E","vendor":"Sensaphone","product_type":"physical","created_at":"2026-02-18T01:55:27-05:00","handle":"ims-solution-indoor-temperature-sensors","updated_at":"2026-02-18T01:55:27-05:00","published_at":"2026-02-18T01:55:12-05:00","template_suffix":null,"published_scope":"global","tags":"BRAND__Sensaphone, CAT__Temperature Sensors__VAL, OLD__237__ID, TYPE__physical","status":"active","admin_graphql_api_id":"gid:\/\/shopify\/Product\/10201320292666","variants":[{"id":53038684209466,"product_id":10201320292666,"title":"Room Temperature Sensor \u00b0F","price":"89.00","position":1,"inventory_policy":"continue","compare_at_price":null,"option1":"Room Temperature Sensor \u00b0F","option2":null,"option3":null,"created_at":"2026-02-18T01:55:27-05:00","updated_at":"2026-02-18T01:55:28-05:00","taxable":true,"barcode":"","fulfillment_service":"manual","grams":