[2026-02-18 07:55:34] [INFO] Product variant images has been updated - Shopidy ID - 10201320358202 - BC id=241 => {"product":{"id":10201320358202,"title":"IMS Solution Mini Temperature Sensor","body_html":"\u003Ch4\u003EMonitor temperature in tight locations\u003C\/h4\u003E\n\u003Cul\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003EMeasures temperatures from 5\u00b0 to 140\u00b0F | -15\u00b0 to 60\u00b0C\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003EAccurate to \u00b1 3\u00b0F\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003ESmall size allows placement in tight locations\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003ERequires RJ45 patch cable to connect sensor to Sensaphone\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\u003Cspan style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003EFor use in clean, indoor environments\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003C\/ul\u003E\u003Cp style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003EThe IMS Mini Temperature Sensor is used exclusively with the Sensaphone IMS systems to measure and provide real time air temperatures from 5\u00b0 to 140\u00b0F. The system will go into alarm when the temperature falls outside of the programmed high or low limit. The sensor comes in a small black enclosure that can be mounted in tight locations such as inside of server racks. The sensor may be secured inside equipment using double-sided tape (included) or with tie-wraps. The connection from the interface to the IMS system can use an existing CAT5 network wiring infrastructure, which powers the sensor and allows it to be installed in locations away from the IMS host device.\u003C\/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E\u003C!-- pagebreak --\u003E\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/p\u003E\n\u003Ch4\u003E\u003Cspan\u003ETechnical Specifications\u003Cbr\u003E\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/h4\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ESensor Temperature Range:\u003C\/strong\u003E 5\u00b0 to 140\u00b0F | 0\u00b0 to 60\u00b0C\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EAccuracy:\u003C\/strong\u003E 3\u00b0F | 1.7\u00b0C \u00a0\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EConnection:\u003C\/strong\u003E RJ45\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EHousing:\u003C\/strong\u003E Plastic\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EDimensions:\u003C\/strong\u003E 2.1 x .6 x 1.4\" | 54 x 15 x 35mm\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ESensor Series:\u003C\/strong\u003E IMS Solution\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/p\u003E","vendor":"Sensaphone","product_type":"physical","created_at":"2026-02-18T01:55:33-05:00","handle":"ims-solution-mini-temperature-sensor","updated_at":"2026-02-18T01:55:33-05:00","published_at":"2026-02-18T01:55:30-05:00","template_suffix":null,"published_scope":"global","tags":"BRAND__Sensaphone, CAT__Temperature Sensors__VAL, OLD__241__ID, TYPE__physical","status":"active","admin_graphql_api_id":"gid:\/\/shopify\/Product\/10201320358202","variants":[{"id":53038684569914,"product_id":10201320358202,"title":"Mini Temperature Sensor \u00b0F","price":"69.00","position":1,"inventory_policy":"continue","compare_at_price":null,"option1":"Mini Temperature Sensor \u00b0F","option2":null,"option3":null,"created_at":"2026-02-18T01:55:33-05:00","updated_at":"2026-02-18T01:55:33-05:00","taxable":true,"barcode":"","fulfillment_service":"manual","grams":0,"inventory_management":"shopify","requires_shipping":true,"sku":"IMS-4812E","weight":0,"weight_unit":"lb","inventory_item_id":55065788776762,"inventory_quantity":0,"old_inventory_quantity":0,"admin_graphql_api_id":"gid:\/\/shopify\/ProductVariant\/53038684569914","image_id":null},{"id":53038684602682,"product_id":10201320358202,"title":"Mini Temperature Sensor \u00b0C","price":"69.00","position":2,"inventory_policy":"continue","compare_at_price":null,"option1":"Mini Temperature Sensor \u00b0C","option2":null,"option3":null,"created_at":"2026-02-18T01:55:33-05:00","updated_at":"2026-02-18T01:55:33-05:00","taxable":true,"barcode":"","fulfillment_service":"manual","grams":0,"inventory_management":"shopify","requires_shipping":true,"sku":"IMS-4812E-C","weight":0,"weight_unit":