[2026-02-18 07:55:54] [INFO] Product variant images has been updated - Shopidy ID - 10201320620346 - BC id=247 => {"product":{"id":10201320620346,"title":"IMS Solution Temperature Sensor w\/ External Probe","body_html":"\u003Ch3\u003EEasy temperature monitoring\u003C\/h3\u003E\n\u003Cul\u003E\n\u003Cli style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003EMeasures temperature from 32\u00b0 to 176\u00b0F | 0\u00b0 to 80\u00b0C\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003EAccurate to \u00b1 3\u00b0F\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003EExternal probe allows monitoring of refrigerator or dirty environments\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003ERequires RJ45 patch cable to connect sensor to Sensaphone\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003C\/ul\u003E\u003Cp style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003EThe IMS Temperature Sensor with External Probe is used exclusively with the Sensaphone IMS systems to measure and provide real time temperatures from 32\u00b0 to 176\u00b0F or 0\u00b0 to 80\u00b0C in difficult environments or in areas where a traditional sensor won\u2019t fit. The temperature sensing probe is attached to the sensor by 12\u2019 of wire which allows it to be placed inside a refrigerator or in a dirty or humid environment while still keeping the sensor\u2019s circuitry clean. The system will go into alarm when the temperature falls outside of the programmed high or low limit. The sensor may be secured using double-sided tape (included) or with tie-wraps. The connection from the interface to the IMS system can use an existing CAT5 network wiring infrastructure, which powers the sensor and allows it to be installed in locations away from the IMS host device.\u003C\/p\u003E\n\u003Ch3\u003E\u003Cspan\u003ETechnical Specifications\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/h3\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ESensor Temperature Range:\u003C\/strong\u003E 32\u00b0 to 176\u00b0F | 0\u00b0 to 80\u00b0C\u00a0\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EAccuracy:\u003C\/strong\u003E 3\u00b0F | 1.7\u00b0C\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EConnection:\u003C\/strong\u003E RJ45\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EHousing:\u003C\/strong\u003E Plastic\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EDimensions:\u003C\/strong\u003E 2.1 x 1.3 x .6\" | 53 x 33 x 15mm\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ESensor Series:\u003C\/strong\u003E IMS Solution\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/p\u003E\n\u003Ch3\u003E\u003Cspan\u003EDownloads\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/h3\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\u003Ca href=\"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0987\/4738\/4122\/files\/CS_IMS-4816E.pdf\"\u003E\u003Cspan\u003EIMS Solution Temperature Sensor w\/ External Probe Sales Brochure\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/a\u003E\u003C\/p\u003E","vendor":"Sensaphone","product_type":"physical","created_at":"2026-02-18T01:55:51-05:00","handle":"ims-solution-temperature-sensor-w-external-probe","updated_at":"2026-02-18T01:55:52-05:00","published_at":"2026-02-18T01:55:48-05:00","template_suffix":null,"published_scope":"global","tags":"BRAND__Sensaphone, CAT__Temperature Sensors__VAL, MAINSKU__IMS-4816E, OLD__247__ID, TYPE__physical","status":"active","admin_graphql_api_id":"gid:\/\/shopify\/Product\/10201320620346","variants":[{"id":53038688010554,"product_id":10201320620346,"title":"Default Title","price":"109.00","position":1,"inventory_policy":"continue","compare_at_price":null,"option1":"Default Title","option2":null,"option3":null,"created_at":"2026-02-18T01:55:52-05:00","updated_at":"2026-02-18T01:55:52-05:00","taxable":true,"barcode":"","fulfillment_service":"manual","grams":0,"inventory_management":"shopify","requires_shipping":true,"sku":"IMS-4816E","weight":0,"weight_unit":"lb","inventory_item_id":55065792217402,"inventory_quantity":0,"old_inventory_quantity":0,"admin_graphql_api_id":"gid:\/\/shopify\/ProductVariant\/53038688010554","image_id":null}],"options":[{"id":12742212518202,"product_id":10201320620346,"name":"Title","position":1,"values":["Default Title"]}],"images":[{"id":55073541062970,"alt":"247_main_