[2026-02-18 07:56:10] [INFO] Product variant images has been updated - Shopidy ID - 10201320751418 - BC id=248 => {"product":{"id":10201320751418,"title":"IMS Solution Room Humidity Sensor","body_html":"\u003Ch4\u003EMonitor humidity levels\u003C\/h4\u003E\n\u003Cul\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003EMeasures humidity levels from 0% to 100% or 5% to 95%\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003EAccurate to +\/- 3%\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003EMay be mounted either on a wall or to a single-gang electrical box\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003EOptional LCD displays humidity level\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003ESet high or low humidity limit by programming the Sensaphone\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003ESensaphone will go into alarm when humidity exceeds limit\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\u003Cspan style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003ERJ45 patch cable powers and connects sensor to Sensaphone (not included)\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003C\/ul\u003E\u003Cp style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003EThe IMS Humidity Sensors are used exclusively with the Sensaphone IMS systems to measure and provide real time humidity levels. When the humidity falls outside of the Sensaphone\u2019s programmed high or low limit, the user will receive an alarm which displays or reads the current humidity value. The sensor can be programed to detect humidity levels from 0 to 100% or 5 to 95% RH. The low profile enclosures allow the sensors to be placed in a single gang electrical box or mounted directly to the wall. It is ideal for clean indoor applications such as a computer room, home, office, museum or hospital. A LCD screen on the front of the sensor displays the humidity level. The connection from the interface to the IMS system can use an existing CAT5 network wiring infrastructure, which powers the sensor and allows it to be installed in locations away from the IMS host device.\u003C\/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E\u003C!-- pagebreak --\u003E\u003C\/s