[2026-02-18 07:56:21] [INFO] Product variant images has been updated - Shopidy ID - 10201320849722 - BC id=250 => {"product":{"id":10201320849722,"title":"IMS Solution Zone Water Detection Sensor","body_html":"\u003Ch3\u003EWidespread water detection\u003C\/h3\u003E\n\u003Cul\u003E\n\u003Cli style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003EDetects water on a floor or false ceiling\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003ESends Sensaphone into alarm when water is detected\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003EIncludes 10\u2019 of water sensing rope\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003EUp to nine additional lengths of water rope can be added for an expanded the water detection area\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003ECommon uses include: burst pipes that leak water, leaking AC unit, bad HVAC compressor, any water leak\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\u003Cspan style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003ERequired RJ45 patch cable powers and connects sensor to Sensaphone\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003C\/ul\u003E\u003Cp style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003EThe IMS Zone Water Detection Sensor is used exclusively with the Sensaphone IMS systems to monitor for the presence of water on a floor or in a false ceiling. When the included 10\u2019 water rope comes in contact with water, it will trigger the Sensaphone to go into alarm. This sensor is ideal for use in homes, businesses or anywhere that is susceptible to flooding or water leaks. The connection from the interface to the IMS system can use an existing CAT5 network wiring infrastructure, which powers the sensor and allows it to be installed in locations away from the IMS host device.\u003C\/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\u003C!-- pagebreak --\u003E\u003C\/p\u003E\n\u003Ch3\u003E\u003Cspan\u003ETechnical Specifications\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/h3\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EConnection:\u003C\/strong\u003E RJ45\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003E