[2026-02-18 07:56:34] [INFO] Product variant images has been updated - Shopidy ID - 10201321013562 - BC id=252 => {"product":{"id":10201321013562,"title":"IMS Solution External Power Failure Sensor","body_html":"\u003Ch3\u003EPower outage monitoring\u003C\/h3\u003E\n\u003Cul\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003ESimply plug this sensor into any outlet (110 volt AC) circuit needing to be monitored\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003ESends Sensaphone into alarm when power loss is detected\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003ECan monitor status of a server rack or remote UPS\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003EMeasures current voltage in the circuit\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003EAny failed generator starts are reported\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003ERequired RJ45 patch cable powers and connects sensor to Sensaphone\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003C\/ul\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan\u003EThe IMS External Power Failure Sensor is used exclusively with the Sensaphone IMS\u00a0to monitor for the loss of power wherever it is plugged in.\u00a0It reports any loss of power and measures the current voltage in the circuit, allowing you to know the status of things like individual server racks or a remote UPS.\u00a0When the sensor detects power failure, it will communicate the failure back to the IMS system. Users will receive an alarm via phone, text message or email.\u00a0The sensor can be plugged into any 110 volt AC outlet.\u00a0The connection from the interface to the IMS system can use an existing CAT5 network wiring infrastructure, which powers the sensor and allows it to be installed in locations away from the IMS host device.\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E\u003C!-- pagebreak --\u003E\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/p\u003E\n\u003Ch3\u003E\u003Cspan\u003ETechnical Specifications\u003Cbr\u003E\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/h3\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ERange:\u003C\/strong\u003E 0250 VAC, 50\/60 Hz\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EAccuracy:\u003C\/strong\u003E 2%\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EPower Connection:\u003C\/strong\u003E Universal IEC-320 power inlet\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EIMS Connection:\u003C\/strong\u003E RJ45\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EHousing:\u003C\/strong\u003E Black plastic with mounting ears\u003C\/span\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/p\u003E\n\u003Ch3\u003E\u003Cspan\u003EDownloads\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/h3\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\u003Ca href=\"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0987\/4738\/4122\/files\/CS_IMS-4840E.pdf\"\u003E\u003Cspan\u003EIMS Solution External Power Failure Sensor Sales Brochure\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/a\u003E\u003C\/p\u003E","vendor":"Sensaphone","product_type":"physical","created_at":"2026-02-18T01:56:32-05:00","handle":"ims-solution-external-power-failure-sensor","updated_at":"2026-02-18T01:56:33-05:00","published_at":"2026-02-18T01:56:27-05:00","template_suffix":null,"published_scope":"global","tags":"BRAND__Sensaphone, CAT__Power Sensors__VAL, MAINSKU__IMS-4840E, OLD__252__ID, TYPE__physical","status":"active","admin_graphql_api_id":"gid:\/\/shopify\/Product\/10201321013562","variants":[{"id":53038689976634,"product_id":10201321013562,"title":"Default Title","price":"139.00","position":1,"inventory_policy":"continue","compare_at_price":null,"option1":"Default Title","option2":null,"option3":null,"created_at":"2026-02-18T01:56:33-05:00","updated_at":"2026-02-18T01:56:33-05:00","taxable":true,"barcode":"","fulfillment_service":"manual","grams":0,"inventory_management":"shopify","requires_shipping":true,"sku":"IMS-4840E","weight":0,"weight_unit":"lb","inventory_item_id":55065794183482,"inventory_quantity":0,"old_inventory_quantity":0,"admin_graphql_api_id":"gid:\/\/shopify\/ProductVariant\/53038689976634","image_id":null}],"options":[{"id":12742212911418,"product_id":10201321013562,"name":"Title","position":1,"values":["Default Title"]}],"images":[{"id":55073544569146,"alt":"252_main_image_0","position":1,"product_id":10201321013562,"created_at":"2026-02-18T