[2026-02-18 07:56:44] [INFO] Product variant images has been updated - Shopidy ID - 10201321144634 - BC id=253 => {"product":{"id":10201321144634,"title":"IMS Solution Dry Contact Interface","body_html":"\u003Ch3\u003EConnect to any NO\/NC Contact\u003C\/h3\u003E\n\u003Cul\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003EConnect your IMS system to any third party Normally dry contact type sensor or equipment\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003EIdeal for connecting to UPS systems or equipment that has a bulit in alarm. The Sensaphone system can remotely provide notification if it goes into alarm.\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003C\/ul\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003EThe IMS Dry Contact Sensor is used exclusively with the Sensaphone IMS system \u003C\/span\u003Eto interface with any normally open or normally closed dry contact. When the contact switches position the sensor will communicate the change back to the IMS system and users will receive an alarm via phone, text message or email.\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003EIt is ideal for monitoring the alarm outputs of other devices such as a UPS, power distribution unit, fire alarm panel, automatic transfer switch or security system\u003C\/span\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E. \u003C\/span\u003E\u003Cspan\u003EThe connection from the interface to the IMS system can use an existing CAT5 network wiring infrastructure, which powers the sensor and allows it to be installed in locations away from the IMS host device.\u003C\/span\u003E\n\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E\u003C!-- pagebreak --\u003E\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/p\u003E\n\u003Ch3\u003E\u003Cspan\u003ETechnical Specifications\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/h3\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EOperating Temperature:\u003C\/strong\u003E 32\u00b0 to 122\u00b0F | 0\u00b0 to 50\u00b0C\u00a0\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EInput:\u003C\/strong\u003E Normally open or normally closed dry contact\u00a0\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ESource\/Sense Voltage:\u003C\/strong\u003E 14VDC\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EConnection:\u003C\/strong\u003E RJ45\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EHousing:\u003C\/strong\u003E Plastic\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EDimensions:\u003C\/strong\u003E 3.3 x 4.2 x 1.3\" | 84 x 107 x 33mm\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ESensor Series:\u003C\/strong\u003E IMS Solution\u003C\/span\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/p\u003E\n\u003Ch3\u003E\u003Cspan\u003EDownloads\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/h3\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\u003Ca href=\"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0987\/4738\/4122\/files\/CS_IMS-4850E.pdf\"\u003E\u003Cspan\u003EIMS Solution Dry Contact Interface Sales Brochure\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/a\u003E\u003C\/p\u003E","vendor":"Sensaphone","product_type":"physical","created_at":"2026-02-18T01:56:42-05:00","handle":"ims-solution-dry-contact-interface","updated_at":"2026-02-18T01:56:42-05:00","published_at":"2026-02-18T01:56:38-05:00","template_suffix":null,"published_scope":"global","tags":"BRAND__Sensaphone, CAT__Other__VAL, MAINSKU__IMS-4850E, OLD__253__ID, TYPE__physical","status":"active","admin_graphql_api_id":"gid:\/\/shopify\/Product\/10201321144634","variants":[{"id":53038690468154,"product_id":10201321144634,"title":"Default Title","price":"62.00","position":1,"inventory_policy":"continue","compare_at_price":null,"option1":"Default Title","option2":null,"option3":null,"created_at":"2026-02-18T01:56:42-05:00","updated_at":"2026-02-18T01:56:43-05:00","taxable":true,"barcode":"","fulfillment_service":"manual","grams":0,"inventory_management":"shopify","requires_shipping":true,"sku":"IMS-4850E","weight":0,"weight_unit":"lb","inventory_item_id":55065794675002,"inventory_quantity":0,"old_inventory_quantity":0,"admin_graphql_api_id":"gid:\/\/shopify\/ProductVariant\/53038690468154","image_id":null}],"options":[{"id":12742213042490,"product_id":10201321144634,"name":"Title","position":1,"values":["Default Title"]}],"images":[{"id":55073545781562,"alt":"253_main_image_0","position":1,"product_id":102