[2026-02-18 07:56:53] [INFO] Product variant images has been updated - Shopidy ID - 10201321242938 - BC id=254 => {"product":{"id":10201321242938,"title":"IMS Solution 4-20mA Interface","body_html":"\u003Ch3\u003EMonitor the output of a 4-20mA transducer\u003C\/h3\u003E\n\u003Cul\u003E\n\u003Cli style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003EInterfaces IMS system with any 4-20mA transducer\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003ESet high and low limits of transducer by programming the Sensaphone\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003ESensaphone will go into alarm when transducer level exceeds limit\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\u003Cspan style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003ERequired RJ45 patch cable powers and connects interface to Sensaphone\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003C\/ul\u003E\u003Cp style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003EThe IMS 4-20mA Interface is used exclusively with the Sensaphone IMS system system to interface with any third party transducer that outputs a 4-20mA signal. The interface will measure and provide real time values to to the IMS system. When the level falls outside of the IMS\u2019s programmed high or low limit, the user will receive an alarm which displays or reads the current value. The connection from the interface to the IMS system can use an existing CAT5 network wiring infrastructure, which allows it to be installed in locations away from the IMS host device.\u003C\/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E\u003C!-- pagebreak --\u003E\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/p\u003E\n\u003Ch3\u003E\u003Cspan\u003ETechnical Specifications\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/h3\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EOperating Temperature:\u003C\/strong\u003E 32\u00b0 to 122\u00b0F | 0\u00b0 to 50\u00b0C\u00a0\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ECurrent Limit:\u003C\/strong\u003E 50mA\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EConnection:\u003C\/strong\u003E RJ45\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EHousing:\u003C\/strong\u003E Plastic\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EDimensions:\u003C\/strong\u003E 3.3 x 4.2 x 1.3\" | 84 x 107 x 33mm\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ESensor Series:\u003C\/strong\u003E IMS Solution\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/p\u003E\n\u003Ch3\u003E\u003Cspan\u003EDownloads\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/h3\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\u003Ca href=\"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0987\/4738\/4122\/files\/CS_IMS-4851E.pdf\"\u003E\u003Cspan\u003EIMS Solution 4-20mA Interface Sales Brochure\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/a\u003E\u003C\/p\u003E","vendor":"Sensaphone","product_type":"physical","created_at":"2026-02-18T01:56:52-05:00","handle":"ims-solution-4-20ma-interface","updated_at":"2026-02-18T01:56:52-05:00","published_at":"2026-02-18T01:56:46-05:00","template_suffix":null,"published_scope":"global","tags":"BRAND__Sensaphone, CAT__Other__VAL, MAINSKU__IMS-4851E, OLD__254__ID, TYPE__physical","status":"active","admin_graphql_api_id":"gid:\/\/shopify\/Product\/10201321242938","variants":[{"id":53038690894138,"product_id":10201321242938,"title":"Default Title","price":"159.00","position":1,"inventory_policy":"continue","compare_at_price":null,"option1":"Default Title","option2":null,"option3":null,"created_at":"2026-02-18T01:56:52-05:00","updated_at":"2026-02-18T01:56:52-05:00","taxable":true,"barcode":"","fulfillment_service":"manual","grams":0,"inventory_management":"shopify","requires_shipping":true,"sku":"IMS-4851E","weight":0,"weight_unit":"lb","inventory_item_id":55065795100986,"inventory_quantity":0,"old_inventory_quantity":0,"admin_graphql_api_id":"gid:\/\/shopify\/ProductVariant\/53038690894138","image_id":null}],"options":[{"id":12742213173562,"product_id":10201321242938,"name":"Title","position":1,"values":["Default Title"]}],"images":[{"id":55073546633530,"alt":"254_main_image_0","position":1,"product_id":10201321242938,"created_at":"2026-02-18T01:56:52-05:00","updated_at":"2026-02-18T01:56:52-05:00","admin_graphql_api_id":"gid:\/\/shopify\/MediaImage\/45112734417210","width":1000,"height":909,"src":"ht