[2026-02-18 07:57:02] [INFO] Product variant images has been updated - Shopidy ID - 10201321308474 - BC id=255 => {"product":{"id":10201321308474,"title":"IMS Solution Magnetic Reed Door and Window Switch","body_html":"\u003Ch3\u003EDetect unauthorized entry or intrusion\u003C\/h3\u003E\n\u003Cul\u003E\n\u003Cli style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003EDetects when a door or window is opened or closed\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003ESends Sensaphone into alarm when door or window condition has changed\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003EEasily mounted with included hardware\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003ERequired RJ45 patch cable powers and connects sensor to Sensaphone\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003EMay be mounted either on a wall or rest on the floor - switch is mounted to doors or windows you wish to monitor.\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003C\/ul\u003E\u003Cp style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003EThe IMS Magnetic Reed Door and Window Switch is used exclusively with the Sensaphone IMS system system to monitor for any unauthorized entry or intrusion. When the door or window is opened or closed, the sensor will trigger the Sensaphone to go into alarm. The switch is usually installed to function in a normally closed position when the door or window is closed. The complete Magnetic Reed Switch assembly comes in two main parts: a magnet in a plastic housing, and a switch with screw terminals in another, separate plastic housing. It mounts to the door or window with the included hardware. The connection from the sensor to the IMS system can use an existing CAT5 network wiring infrastructure, which powers the sensor and allows it to be installed in locations away from the IMS host device.\u003C\/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E\u003C!-- pagebreak --\u003E\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/p\u003E\n\u003Ch3\u003E\u003Cspan\u003ETechnical Specifications\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/h3\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EBridge Input:\u003C\/strong\u003E Normally Open or Normally Closed Contact\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ESource\/Sense Voltage:\u003C\/strong\u003E 14VDC\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EConnection:\u003C\/strong\u003E RJ45\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EHousing:\u003C\/strong\u003E Plastic\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EDimensions:\u003C\/strong\u003E 2.1 x 1.3 x .6\" | 53 x 33 x 15mm\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ESensor Series:\u003C\/strong\u003E IMS Solution\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/p\u003E\n\u003Ch3\u003E\u003Cspan\u003EDownloads\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/h3\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\u003Ca href=\"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0987\/4738\/4122\/files\/CS_IMS-4860E.pdf\"\u003E\u003Cspan\u003EIMS Solution Magnetic Reed Door and Window Switch Sales Brochure\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/a\u003E\u003C\/p\u003E","vendor":"Sensaphone","product_type":"physical","created_at":"2026-02-18T01:57:00-05:00","handle":"ims-solution-magnetic-reed-door-and-window-switch","updated_at":"2026-02-18T01:57:01-05:00","published_at":"2026-02-18T01:56:56-05:00","template_suffix":null,"published_scope":"global","tags":"BRAND__Sensaphone, CAT__Security__VAL, MAINSKU__IMS-4860E, OLD__255__ID, TYPE__physical","status":"active","admin_graphql_api_id":"gid:\/\/shopify\/Product\/10201321308474","variants":[{"id":53038691189050,"product_id":10201321308474,"title":"Default Title","price":"59.00","position":1,"inventory_policy":"continue","compare_at_price":null,"option1":"Default Title","option2":null,"option3":null,"created_at":"2026-02-18T01:57:01-05:00","updated_at":"2026-02-18T01:57:01-05:00","taxable":true,"barcode":"","fulfillment_service":"manual","grams":0,"inventory_management":"shopify","requires_shipping":true,"sku":"IMS-4860E","weight":0,"weight_unit":"lb","inventory_item_id":55065795395898,"inventory_quantity":0,"old_inventory_quantity":0,"admin_graphql_api_id":"gid:\/\/shopify\/ProductVariant\/53038691189050","image_id":null}],"options":[{"id":12742213239098,"product_i