[2026-02-18 07:57:10] [INFO] Product variant images has been updated - Shopidy ID - 10201321341242 - BC id=256 => {"product":{"id":10201321341242,"title":"IMS Solution Infrared Motion Detection Sensor","body_html":"\u003Ch3\u003EMonitor for the movement of warm bodies\u003C\/h3\u003E\n\u003Cul\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003EDual-element passive infrared intrusion detector\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003EReduces false alarms by eliminating background noises and nuisance stimuli\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003EVariable pulse-count adjustment, thus making it adaptable for use both inside and outside of server\/equipment rooms\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003ECompatible with IMS-1000E or IMS-4000E\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003EConnects to host device via RJ-45 patch cable\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003C\/ul\u003E\u003Cp style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003EThe IMS Infrared Motion Detection Sensor is used exclusively with the Sensaphone IMS system system to monitor for the movement of warm bodies in a room. When a person enters the room, the sensor will trigger the Sensaphone to go into alarm. The range is a maximum of 40 feet directly ahead of, and approximately 20 feet to either side of the detector at 40 feet distance. The sensor mounts to the wall with the included hardware. The connection from the sensor to the IMS system can use an existing CAT5 network wiring infrastructure, which powers the sensor and allows it to be installed in locations away from the IMS host device.\u003C\/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E\u003C!-- pagebreak --\u003E\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/p\u003E\n\u003Ch3\u003E\u003Cspan\u003ETechnical Specifications\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/h3\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EOperating Range:\u003C\/strong\u003E -4\u00b0 to 140\u00b0F | -20\u00b0 to 60\u00b0C\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EConnection:\u003C\/strong\u003E RJ45\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EHousing:\u003C\/strong\u003E Plastic\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EDimensions:\u003C\/strong\u003E 3.8 x 1.8 x 2.5\" | 97 x 63 x 47mm\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ESensor Series:\u003C\/strong\u003E IMS Solution\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/p\u003E\n\u003Ch3\u003E\u003Cspan\u003EDownloads\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/h3\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\u003Ca href=\"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0987\/4738\/4122\/files\/CS_IMS-4861E.pdf\"\u003E\u003Cspan\u003EIMS Solution Infrared Motion Detection Sensor Sales Brochure\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/a\u003E\u003C\/p\u003E","vendor":"Sensaphone","product_type":"physical","created_at":"2026-02-18T01:57:08-05:00","handle":"ims-solution-infrared-motion-detection-sensor","updated_at":"2026-02-18T01:57:09-05:00","published_at":"2026-02-18T01:57:06-05:00","template_suffix":null,"published_scope":"global","tags":"BRAND__Sensaphone, CAT__Security__VAL, MAINSKU__IMS-4861E, OLD__256__ID, TYPE__physical","status":"active","admin_graphql_api_id":"gid:\/\/shopify\/Product\/10201321341242","variants":[{"id":53038691352890,"product_id":10201321341242,"title":"Default Title","price":"89.00","position":1,"inventory_policy":"continue","compare_at_price":null,"option1":"Default Title","option2":null,"option3":null,"created_at":"2026-02-18T01:57:09-05:00","updated_at":"2026-02-18T01:57:09-05:00","taxable":true,"barcode":"","fulfillment_service":"manual","grams":0,"inventory_management":"shopify","requires_shipping":true,"sku":"IMS-4861E","weight":0,"weight_unit":"lb","inventory_item_id":55065795559738,"inventory_quantity":0,"old_inventory_quantity":0,"admin_graphql_api_id":"gid:\/\/shopify\/ProductVariant\/53038691352890","image_id":null}],"options":[{"id":12742213271866,"product_id":10201321341242,"name":"Title","position":1,"values":["Default Title"]}],"images":[{"id":55073548271930,"alt":"256_main_image_0","position":1,"product_id":10201321341242,"created_at":"2026-02-18T01:57:08-05:00","updated_at":"2026-02-18T01:57:08-05:00","admin_graphql_api_id":"gid:\/\/shopify\/MediaImage\/45112735990074","width":1000,"height":1000,"src":"https:\/\/cdn.s