[2026-02-18 07:57:18] [INFO] Product variant images has been updated - Shopidy ID - 10201321406778 - BC id=257 => {"product":{"id":10201321406778,"title":"IMS Solution Smoke Detection Sensor","body_html":"\u003Ch3\u003ESmoke Detection\u003C\/h3\u003E\n\u003Cul\u003E\n\u003Cli style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003EUses a photoelectric smoke sensing unit\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003EUncommon for household smoke such as cigarette smoke or normal cooking smoke to cause an alarm\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003ESends Sensaphone into alarm when smoke is detected\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\u003Cspan style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003ERequired RJ45 patch cable powers and connects sensor to Sensaphone\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003C\/ul\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003EThe IMS Smoke Detection Sensor is used exclusively with the Sensaphone IMS system \u003C\/span\u003Eto monitor for the presence of smoke. When the sensor detects smoke, it will trigger the Sensaphone to go into alarm and also sound an audible horn. The connection from the sensor to the IMS system can use an existing CAT5 network wiring infrastructure, which powers the sensor and allows it to be installed in locations away from the IMS host device.\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv\u003E\u00a0\u003C\/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E\u003C!-- pagebreak --\u003E\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/p\u003E\n\u003Ch3\u003E\u003Cspan\u003ETechnical Specifications\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/h3\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EOperating Temperature:\u003C\/strong\u003E 40\u00b0 to 100\u00b0F | 4\u00b0 to 37\u00b0C\u00a0\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EConnection:\u003C\/strong\u003E RJ45\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EHousing:\u003C\/strong\u003E Plastic\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EDimensions:\u003C\/strong\u003E 6.5 diameter x 2.6\" | 165 x 66mm\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ESensor Series:\u003C\/strong\u003E IMS Solution\u003C\/span\u0