[2026-02-18 07:57:30] [INFO] Product variant images has been updated - Shopidy ID - 10201321472314 - BC id=258 => {"product":{"id":10201321472314,"title":"IMS Solution Air Flow Sensor","body_html":"\u003Ch3\u003EMonitor the presence or absence of cool moving air\u003C\/h3\u003E\n\u003Cul\u003E\n\u003Cli style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003EMeasures relative air flow passing over the sensor from 0 to 100%\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003ESet high and low airflow limits by programming the Sensaphone\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003ESensaphone will go into alarm when air flow level exceeds the high or low limit\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003EEasily mounted with included Velcro, double side tape or tie wraps\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003ERequired RJ45 patch cable powers and connects sensor to Sensaphone\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003C\/ul\u003E\u003Cp style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003EThe IMS Air Flow Sensor is used exclusively with the Sensaphone IMS system system to measure and provide real time air flow values. It reports the relative air flow from 0 to 100% allowing you to monitor the operation of your cooling and ventilation systems. When the air flow level falls outside of the Sensaphone\u2019s programmed high or low limit, the user will receive an alarm which displays or reads the current air flow value. The connection from the sensor to the IMS system can use an existing CAT5 network wiring infrastructure, which powers the sensor and allows it to be installed in locations away from the IMS host device.\u003C\/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E\u003C!-- pagebreak --\u003E\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/p\u003E\n\u003Ch3\u003E\u003Cspan\u003ETechnical Specifications:\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/h3\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EOperating Temperature:\u003C\/strong\u003E 32\u00b0 to 80\u00b0F | 0\u00b0 to 27\u00b0C\u00a0\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ESensing Range:\u003C\/strong\u003E Approximately 0 to 2,000 fpm\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EConnection:\u003C\/strong\u003E RJ45\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EHousing:\u003C\/strong\u003E Plastic\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EDimensions:\u003C\/strong\u003E 4.2 x 1.6 x 0.9\" | 106 x 40 x 23mm\u00a0\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ESensor Series:\u003C\/strong\u003E IMS Solution\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/p\u003E\n\u003Ch3\u003E\u003Cspan\u003EDownloads\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/h3\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E\u003Ca href=\"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0987\/4738\/4122\/files\/CS_IMS-4863.pdf\"\u003EIMS Solution Air Flow Sensor Sales Brochure\u003C\/a\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Ca href=\"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0987\/4738\/4122\/files\/IMS-4863_AirflowSensorInstructions.pdf\"\u003EIMS Solution Air Flow Sensor Instructions\u003C\/a\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/p\u003E","vendor":"Sensaphone","product_type":"physical","created_at":"2026-02-18T01:57:29-05:00","handle":"ims-solution-air-flow-sensor","updated_at":"2026-02-18T01:57:29-05:00","published_at":"2026-02-18T01:57:22-05:00","template_suffix":null,"published_scope":"global","tags":"BRAND__Sensaphone, CAT__Other__VAL, MAINSKU__IMS-4863E, OLD__258__ID, TYPE__physical","status":"active","admin_graphql_api_id":"gid:\/\/shopify\/Product\/10201321472314","variants":[{"id":53038691877178,"product_id":10201321472314,"title":"Default Title","price":"119.00","position":1,"inventory_policy":"continue","compare_at_price":null,"option1":"Default Title","option2":null,"option3":null,"created_at":"2026-02-18T01:57:29-05:00","updated_at":"2026-02-18T01:57:30-05:00","taxable":true,"barcode":"","fulfillment_service":"manual","grams":0,"inventory_management":"shopify","requires_shipping":true,"sku":"IMS-4863E","weight":0,"weight_unit":"lb","inventory_item_id":55065796084026,"inventory_quantity":0,"old_inventory_quantity":0,"admin_graphql_api_id":"gid:\/\/shopify\/ProductVariant\/53038691