[2026-02-18 07:58:06] [INFO] Product variant images has been updated - Shopidy ID - 10201321537850 - BC id=266 => {"product":{"id":10201321537850,"title":"Sensaphone WSG30 Wireless Temperature Display","body_html":"\u003Cp style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003EThe Wireless Temperature Display is used exclusively with the Sensaphone WSG30 connects with all Sensaphone 2.8k and RTD type temperature sensors to provide an at-a-glance reading of the current temperature as well as the minimum and maximum temperatures. The display is ideal for any location where onsite staff need a quick, convenient visual reading of the sensor, saving them the time of checking the monitoring system's data.\u003C\/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003EThe Local Temperature Display:\u003C\/p\u003E\n\u003Cul\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003ELogs and displays the highest and lowest temperatures\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003EProvides an audible alarm for out-of-range temperatures\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003EOffers a relay output that can be programmed to turn on a light or siren for additional onsite alarm notifications.\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003C\/ul\u003E\u003Cp style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003EWhen the temperature falls out of the programmed high and low limits, the display triggers an audible alarm, immediately alerting onsite staff of a potential problem. This alarm is in addition to the alerts that the Sensaphone monitoring system sends to designated personnel when temperatures fall out of range.\u003C\/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003EThe\u00a0temperature\u00a0sensor display is easy to program by using the four buttons on the front. It connects to the sensor via screw terminals on the bottom and wirelessly with the Sensaphone WSG30. The display comes with a battery that powers it for up to one year, but you can also use an optional external power supply.\u003C\/p\u003E\n\u003Ch3 style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003ETechnical Specifications\u003C\/h3\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ESensor Temperature Range:\u003C\/strong\u003E \u003Cbr\u003E\u2022 2.8k Room Temperature Sensor: \u003Cspan\u003E0\u00b0 to 120\u00b0F | -17\u00b0 to 49\u00b0C\u003C\/span\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u2022 2.8k Weatherproof Temperature Sensor: \u003Cspan\u003E-20\u00b0 to 176\u00b0F | -28\u00b0 to 80\u00b0C\u003Cbr\u003E\u003C\/span\u003E\u2022 2.8k Ultra Low Temperature Sensor: \u003Cspan\u003E-121\u00b0 to 176\u00b0F | -85\u00b0 to 80\u00b0C\u003Cbr\u003E\u003C\/span\u003E\u2022 1\" RTD Temperature Probe: \u003Cspan\u003E-326\u00b0 to 248\u00b0F | -199\u00b0 to 120\u00b0C \u003C\/span\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u2022 14\" RTD Temperature Probe: \u003Cspan\u003E-326\u00b0 to 248\u00b0F | -199\u00b0 to 120\u00b0C \u003C\/span\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u2022 2.8k Temperatur Sensor in Glass Bead Vial: \u003Cspan\u003E-20\u00b0 to 176\u00b0F | -28\u00b0 to 80\u00b0C\u003Cbr\u003E\u2022 2.8k Temperatur Sensor in Glycol Vial: -20\u00b0 to 176\u00b0F | -28\u00b0 to 80\u00b0C\u003C\/span\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EConnection:\u003C\/strong\u003E\u00a0Wireless\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EDimensions:\u003C\/strong\u003E\u00a03.1 x 3.9 x 1.1\" | 79 x 99 x 28mm\u00a0\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ESensor Series:\u003C\/strong\u003E WSG Wireless\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EOperating Temperature Range:\u003C\/strong\u003E 32\u00b0 to 122\u00b0F | \u003Cspan\u003E\u00a0\u003C\/span\u003E0\u00b0 to 50\u00b0C\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EOperating Humidity:\u003C\/strong\u003E 5- 90% RH non-condensing\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ERange (Indoor\/Urban)\u003C\/strong\u003E: Up to 300\u2019 \u003Cspan\u003E| \u003C\/span\u003E90m\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ETransmit Power Output:\u003C\/strong\u003E 79 mW\u003Cspan\u003E\u00a0 \u003C\/span\u003E(+19 dBm)\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EOperating Frequency:\u003C\/strong\u003E ISM 2.4 GHz\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EDimensions:\u003C\/strong\u003E 4.65 x 3.7 x 1.1\u201d\u003Cspan\u003E\u00a0| \u003C\/span\u003E118 x 94 x 28mm\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EWeight:\u003C\/strong\u003E 0.40 lb. | 181 gm\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EAccuracy:\u003C\/strong\u003E +\/- 1\u00b0F | 0.56\u00b0C\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EPower Supply:\u003C\/strong\u003E 5VDC\u003Cspan\u003E\u00a0 \u003C\/span\u003E1A (optional, part # XFR-0046)\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EBatteries:\u003C\/strong\u003E (2) AA lithium cells will power the sensor for up to 3 years\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EHousing Material:\u003C\/strong\u003E ABS Plastic\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EMounting:\u003C\/strong\u003E 3M Dual Lock Reclosable Fasteners\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003C\/p\u003E\n\u003Ch3 style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003EDownloads:\u003C\/h3\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003E\u003Ca href=\"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0987\/4738\/4122\/files\/CS_FGD-WSG-LCD85.pdf\"\u003ESensaphone WSG30 Wireless Temperature Display with Ultra Low Temperature Sensor Cutsheet\u003C\/a\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Ca href=\"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0987\/4738\/4122\/files\/CS_FGD-WSG-LCDRM.pdf\"\u003ESensaphone WSG30 Wireless Temperature Display Cutsheet\u003C\/a\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Ca href=\"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0987\/4738\/4122\/files\/CS_FGD-WSG_LCDR1.pdf\"\u003ESensaphone WSG30 Wireless Temperature Display with 1\" RTD Cutsheet\u003C\/a\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Ca href=\"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0987\/4738\/4122\/files\/CS_FGD-WSG-LCDR14.pdf\"\u003ESensaphone WSG30 Wireless Temperature Display with 14\" RTD Cutsheet\u003C\/a\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Ca href=\"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0987\/4738\/4122\/files\/CS_FGD-WSG-LCDT.pdf\"\u003ESensaphone WSG30 Wireless Temperature Display with Weatherproof Temperature Sensor Cutsheet\u003C\/a\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Ca href=\"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0987\/4738\/4122\/files\/CS_FGD-WSG-LCDGBV.pdf\"\u003ESensaphone WSG30 Wireless Temperature Display