[2026-02-18 07:58:43] [INFO] Product variant images has been updated - Shopidy ID - 10201321636154 - BC id=267 => {"product":{"id":10201321636154,"title":"Sensaphone Sentry Monitoring System","body_html":"\u003Ch3 style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003E\u003Cspan\u003EA Cellular-Based Monitoring Solution\u2026. No More Telephone Lines\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/strong\u003E\u003C\/h3\u003E\n\u003Cul style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003EA supervised connection assures the Sentry is online and monitoring at all times\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003ECheck sensor status or make programming changes with the Sensaphone mobile App or \u003C\/span\u003E\u003Ca href=\"http:\/\/sensaphone.net\/\"\u003ESensaphone.net\u003C\/a\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E website.\u003C\/span\u003E\n\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003ENotifies an unlimited number of people by e-mail, text message or voice phone calls in the event of an alarm\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003EUp to five external sensors monitor temperature, humidity, water and more\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\u003Cspan\u003ELTE-M Cellular technology ensures device connectivity in difficult locations via AT&amp;T, Verizon, and multiple Canadian carriers.\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003ETemperature sensing range of -109\u00b0 to 115\u00b0F | -85\u00b0 to 57\u00b0C\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003EManage multiple units, make programming changes and access status conditions using a simple, powerful web-based interface\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003ELow cost subscription includes all online hosting, cellular connection fees, and unlimited text, phone and email alerts\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003EContact us before purchasing to confirm cellular coverage\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\u003Cspan\u003EAntenna and SIM card included\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003EMade in USA\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003EAvailable in optional weatherproof NEMA 4X enclosure\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003C\/ul\u003E\u003Cp style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003EThe Sensaphone Sentry Monitoring System offers an easy-to-install, easy-to-configure monitoring solution for locations with no access to a landline or Internet connection. The system monitors up to five different environmental and equipment status conditions including temperature, humidity, power failure and water detection. When the system identifies issues, it instantly sends alerts via phone, text or email over a cellular connection. Users can access information and make system changes from any web-enabled device. No software is required, so installation, integration and management are easy.\u003C\/p\u003E\n\u003Cul style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EINCLUDED\u003C\/strong\u003E: Internal rechargeable battery-backup system will provide 12 hours of continuous monitoring and alerting in the event of a power outage.\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EINCLUDED\u003C\/strong\u003E: Power failure monitoring\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EOPTIONAL\u003C\/strong\u003E: Weatherproof NEMA 4-X enclosure\u003C\/li\u003E\n\u003C\/ul\u003E\u003Ch3 style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ETechnical Specifications:\u003C\/strong\u003E\u003C\/h3\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ECommunication Method\u003C\/strong\u003E:\u003Cbr\u003E4G\/LTE Cellular Modem for use on Verizon, AT&amp;T or Rogers\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ENumber of Inputs\u003C\/strong\u003E:\u003Cbr\u003E5\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EInput Types\u003C\/strong\u003E:\u003Cbr\u003EContact, 2.8K\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ETemperature Sensing Range\u003C\/strong\u003E:\u003Cbr\u003E-109\u00b0 to 115\u00b0F | -85\u00b0 to 57\u00b0C\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EOutput Relay\u003C\/strong\u003E:\u003Cbr\u003EOne low voltage NO\/NC relay output\u003Cbr\u003EManual or automatic alarm switching\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ERemote Access\u003C\/strong\u003E:\u003Cbr\u003EWebsite or mobile app to access status and programming\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ELocal Access\u003C\/strong\u003E:\u003Cbr\u003ELEDs for Alarm Status, Power Status, Online Status, Relay Output Status and Cellular link\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EAlarm Notifications\u003C\/strong\u003E:\u003Cbr\u003EAn unlimited number of email, text or phone calls\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EPower Requirement\u003C\/strong\u003E:\u003Cbr\u003E90-260VAC\/7.5VDC 50\/60Hz 7.5W wall plug-in transformer w\/6\u2019 cord (included)\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EBattery Backup\u003C\/strong\u003E:\u003Cbr\u003E12-Hour rechargeable battery backup\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EPhysical\u003C\/strong\u003E:\u003Cbr\u003E6.1 x 4.7 x 1.4\u201d \u003Cspan\u003E\u00a0\u003C\/span\u003E| \u003Cspan\u003E\u00a0\u003C\/span\u003E155 x 120 x 35 mm)\u003Cbr\u003E1 lb. | .45kg\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EAntenna\u003C\/strong\u003E:\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E5G\/4G Omni Directional Cellular Antenna 50 Ohm, 600-6000MHz Operational 5W (Maximum Input Power) Dipole Terminal Antenna with Hinged SMA(M) Connector\u003Cbr\u003E\u003C\/span\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EAntenna Dimensions:\u003C\/strong\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E168x18x13 mm\u003Cbr\u003E\u003C\/span\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EOperating Temp\u003C\/strong\u003E: \u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E32\u00b0 to 122\u00b0F \u00a0| \u00a00\u00b0 to 50\u00b0C\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/p\u003E\n\u003Ch3\u003E\u003Cspan\u003EDownloads\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/h3\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003E\u003Ca href=\"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0987\/4738\/4122\/files\/Sentry_PremiumCellular.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"\u003E\u003Cspan\u003ESensaphone Sentry Subscription Form\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/a\u003E\u003C\/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\u003Ca href=\"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0987\/4738\/4122\/files\/Sensaphone_Sentry.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"\u003ESensaph